INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('BIcPZBWoTzo', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'How can a Buddhist judge which sutra is the best (GDD-352, Master Sheng Yen)', '');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('AEWMHHKDJds', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'How does one establish and maintain a family (GDD-353, Master Sheng Yen)', '');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('IB-1arwUmHg', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'What circumstances are most suitable to becoming a monastic (GDD-354, Master Sheng Yen)', '');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('XdpK-IVD_JY', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'How we can maintain a modest attitude GDD 355, Master Sheng Yen', 'From a Buddhist perspective, we know that people are basically ordinary, unenlightened, and so of course have faults. We should think of our own faults first and then see if others have good points that we can learn from. We should criticize others less and examine ourselves more. We should also make a compassionate vow for the future, finding ways to help and benefit sentient beings, and then we will feel that there is too much to learn and work for. If we can do this, then we can be very modest.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('dt3ELCJvi9M', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'Is it really possible for a person who vows to be reborn in .... (GDD-356, Master Sheng-Yen)', 'As long as there is attachment to the self, differentiation of the self and self-centeredness, as long as there is a self, a notion of the self, then one is not liberated and there must be karmic effects one has to receive. By reciting Amitabha''s name and thus being reborn in his pure land, we can eliminate our afflictions completely and become liberated. Then we can vow to return to this world to deliver sentient beings, which is in itself accepting karmic retribution actively and therefore amounts to no longer suffering karmic retribution.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('rD7CyLK_OLk', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'Buddhist perspective on sexual discrimination (GDD-357, Master Sheng-Yen)', 'Shakyamuni Buddha never discriminated against women because he believed that bhikshunis and bhikshus were the same and could both attain arhatship. There are great bodhisattvas who are women, like Queen Shrimala, which is very clearly stated in the sutras. The Buddha has compassion and regarded all sentient beings as equal, so how could men and women not be equal?');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('l2bqNCLRoCE', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'Buddhist perspective on organ donation (GDD-361, Master Sheng-Yen)', 'Buddhism does believe that if a person clings to his body, then he cannot be moved before the last breath to avoid adding to their suffering or affecting their ascension to the pure land or rebirth in a good realm of existence. If a person made a vow to donate his organs or was very compassionate, once death is properly determined, removing his organs to save another won''t cause him any harm or vexation and anger.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('r8FX7BFYWFA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'What does sharing others'' joy actually mean (GDD-362, Master Sheng-Yen)', 'Rejoice in others'' merit, one of the ten great vows of Samantabhadra, is rejoicing in other people''s good deeds and good qualities or taking part in someone else''s meritorious deeds. No matter what situation we are in and what position and status we have, we can help people at any opportunity, by using our mental and physical effort, financial resources, influence, and social status.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('IyAWU-z4OV8', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'What actions are in the deceased''s best interest (GDD-364, Master Sheng-Yen)', 'When a hospital pronounces someone dead, that''s when a person''s heartbeat stops, the pulse is gone and the breath stops. In Buddhism, it''s after a person''s spiritual consciousness has left the body that we speak of \"death\". The deceased''s spiritual consciousness is free of the body and unaffected by its cremation. We can benefit the dead best by chanting \"Amitabha Buddha\" to help him gain rebirth in the Western Pure Land.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('rM89mPnjgzE', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'How do we help those on their deathbed who wish to.. ..(GDD-365, Master Sheng-Yen)', 'It''s best to let the dying person pass away in a comfortable manner and without physical burden. In general, let him die peacefully in a lying position. Then ask him to recite the Buddha''s name, and everyone present can chant the Buddha''s name gently and softly to help him. That''s the best way to pass away.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('WNl1JU1ZYNY', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'How to prepare psychologically and adjust one''s attitude .....(GDD-366, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Taking refuge in the Three Jewels means that we identify with and accept the Buddha, Dharma and Sangha, and are willing to live by the Buddha''s teachings cultivating compassion and wisdom. It''s not true that after taking refuge there will be many frightening, scary things awaiting us or that there will be lots of restraints and restrictions; instead it will help us live a more wholesome, peaceful, and down-to-earth life, to be a better human being.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('_i8mj3IJT84', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'Buddhism''s view on the unlucky number 9 (GDD-367, Master Sheng-Yen)', 'Chinese people have Chinese superstitions and foreigners have foreign superstitions. Superstitions have to do with people''s customs, history and cultural background. Instead of keeping telling ourselves, thinking to ourselves that we will have bad luck in a certain year or that things won''t go smoothly, we should become mentally strong and recite the Buddha''s or bodhisattva''s name more often, do more good deeds, and help people more, then there will be less problems.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('G4s4UAESKRk', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'Seeing a bright future in one''s advancing years (GDD-368,  Master Sheng-Yen)', 'Toward the last several years or last period of our life, we should get mentally prepared for the future. We need to be confident and hopeful about the future, and have vows for the future, vowing that everlastingly we want to deliver sentient beings and give of ourselves by following the Buddha''s path, learning the compassion and wisdom of the Buddha.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('9PNwVPO180U', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'Rules for visiting a monastery (GDD-369,  Master Sheng-Yen)', 'Regular monasteries actually don''t have so many elaborate rules of etiquette; there is a lot of flexibility in the monastery. As long as one behaves politely one needs not worry and doesn''t have to feel intimidating when visiting a monastery. If we do not understand the etiquette, we will understand once we go.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('50DtM9OcVBI', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'Why are there more female Buddhist followers (GDD-370,  Master Sheng-Yen)', 'In Taiwan, there are more female than male Buddhist followers because of our social structure and because the work patterns and lifestyles of men and women are not quite the same. In general, women are gentler and more mild-tempered, so under most circumstances they are more likely to accept religious faith. This is not just true in Buddhism.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('TH0_xIf22eg', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'Eating natural foods (GDD-371, Master Sheng-Yen)', 'The current fad of natural, health food happens to coincide with the Buddhist position. While some people promote natural food for health reasons, Buddhism advocates vegetarian food to show compassion toward animals. Even if we cannot stick to vegetarianism, just trying to eat more natural food and cut back on meat can help ourselves become kinder and gentler and develop more compassion.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('A78jiKZeG_o', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'Should Buddhists completely avoid using leather?(GDD-372, Master Sheng-Yen)', 'There are no rules in Buddhism that forbid the use of leather, but it''s best to try to avoid it unless it''s something we need. For example, in the bhikshu and bhikshuni precepts, there is a rule that monastics are allowed to wear straw sandals with leather soles for walking on mountain paths or long distances. Hopefully we can use less leather, but if we use leather when we need to we shouldn''t feel guilty.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('SQsA4tnOWj0', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'How to develop our inner wisdom and compassion (GDD-373, Master Sheng-Yen)', 'If there is something in our mind, then it has obstructions; it cannot be broad and vast, open and clear, and therefore it cannot really have wisdom and compassion. A mind free of obstructions is a mind without distracted thoughts and vexations. When we are not affected or afflicted by our environment, that''s wisdom; with such wisdom, we will have compassion.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('xQmvpZTeCUk', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'Why do good people still suffer retribution?(GDD-374, Master Sheng-Yen)', 'From the perspective of the Buddhadharma, human life and death aren''t limited to one lifetime. We have actually gone through countless rebirths, so sometimes it''s difficult to look at the causes and effects solely at a single lifetime. The best way is to let bygones be bygones while paying attention to our present actions; things that can be dealt with should be dealt with properly. This is more conducive to our physical and mental well-being, and to our own future.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Zes32gJdBAE', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGRnsE_hUi0SHEqtQdjRUI7', 'The emotional life of monastics (GDD-375, Master Sheng-Yen)', 'Sentient beings are sentient because they have feelings, and monastics are no exception. However, the Buddha''s teachings require that we become an awakened or enlightened sentient being, so as to dissolve our own vexations and help relieve others of affliction and suffering.');
INSERT INTO playlist(pid, cid, title, description) VALUES('PLz2LIY6rQQrGPsFu6BDYVCuj9zqq1Kzdn','UCBIGwiecylJsQrhTPBKI4Qw', 'GDD(0326-0350)', '');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('X5qf-nkR3bs', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGPsFu6BDYVCuj9zqq1Kzdn', 'How to harmonize emotion and reason(GDD-0327)', 'Emotion and reason should complement each other and be in balance. Buddhism teaches that we purify our emotion and transform it into compassion, showing concern and sympathy towards others without attachment, as well as use our wisdom to be flexible, accommodating others and adapting to their needs. Applying compassion with wisdom is harmonizing emotion and reason.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('6neYneo0tWA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGPsFu6BDYVCuj9zqq1Kzdn', 'Flying saucers and the Buddhist view of the universe(GDD-0328)', 'Our planet is only a very tiny world among immeasurable, countless worlds in the ten directions of the universe. Buddhism has a very extensive view of the world, and says that worlds arise and perish, with some universes perishing here and others forming there. In every world, sentient beings have different karma and different environments.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Xd3r-we4NrY', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGPsFu6BDYVCuj9zqq1Kzdn', 'The difference between pain and suffering(GDD-0326)', 'Pain is a physical phenomenon experienced with our nerves. Suffering is a mental phenomenon, a psychological thing. Pain is not tantamount to suffering, yet suffering can often cause pain. Our suffering comes from our craving and attachment, and from our unwilling or reluctant to give up or let go. If we are able to readily take up responsibilities, let go of any attachment, and face reality and deal with the situation at hand without running away from it, then we won''t feel suffering in our minds.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('IXVUwn3gTeE', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGPsFu6BDYVCuj9zqq1Kzdn', 'The significance of story of \"The Big Duck and the Small Duck\"(GDD-0331)', 'Big ducks leave large wakes and little ducks leave small wakes. Whether it''s big or small, each duck takes its own path. Everyone has different karma and blessings, so there''s no need to compare ourselves with others and envy others. We should do as much as we can do and learn with peace of mind in our lives.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('SQB5mblWnjc', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGPsFu6BDYVCuj9zqq1Kzdn', 'How do college students select a mentor in Buddhism?(GDD-0333)', 'Studying Buddhist doctrine and practicing are two different things. But it helps to have a clear idea of what Buddhism is about by truly understanding Buddhist doctrine before we start to practice; otherwise we could easily go astray in our practice because we aren''t clear about our direction and the basic principles involved.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('nyi_zsdGvXs', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGPsFu6BDYVCuj9zqq1Kzdn', 'How should women practice spiritually?(GDD-0334)', 'Men and women are fundamentally equal; the Buddha says that all sentient beings have buddha-nature. Therefore, when it comes to spiritual practice, there aren''t different methods for women and men. The methods are the same and the goal is also the same, as are the ideas and views, although differences do arise in some situations.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('QVRJaTgkJT0', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGPsFu6BDYVCuj9zqq1Kzdn', 'Why should we \"generate the mind\"?(GDD-0335)', 'In Buddhism, to \"generate the mind\" means to generate a \"great mind\" or \"vast mind\", meaning generating a bodhisattva mind to do good deeds for the benefit of all sentient beings. It also means to generate a mind of patience and perseverance, meaning that we should not stop until we attain Buddhahood or, at least, that we should continue to do good deeds, do what we should do, and work hard.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('fhtOSpk0TpI', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGPsFu6BDYVCuj9zqq1Kzdn', 'Literary creation and spiritual practice(GDD-0336)', 'A real practitioner doesn''t write just for the sake of writing, but writes to pass on what he knows and has experienced of the Buddhadharma to other people. I express what I have to say using speech and writing that most people can understand, so as to allow people to know what I''m thinking, what I''ve experienced, and what I''ve discovered. My doctorate degree helps me contribute cultural, academic and educational circles, and attract or introduce people to Buddhism.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('eVXtaQS0uSo', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGPsFu6BDYVCuj9zqq1Kzdn', 'What should monastics do when a problem arises at home? \u007F (GDD-337, Master Sheng Yen)', '');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('NhvrDcfSQ30', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGPsFu6BDYVCuj9zqq1Kzdn', 'Introspection and correction (GDD-338, Master Sheng Yen)', 'We should examine our every thought with a sense of shame, and have to keep going so as to discover the mistakes. If we keep discovering mistakes and correcting them, then we may gradually improve ourselves. Chan practice requires us to use the methods of practice to examine our mind, which is the most important. Don''t be afraid of making mistakes; be afraid only of not recognizing mistakes. Don''t be afraid of having bad thoughts; be afraid only of being unaware of having bad thoughts.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('NhvrDcfSQ30', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGPsFu6BDYVCuj9zqq1Kzdn', 'Introspection and correction (GDD-338, Master Sheng Yen)', 'We should examine our every thought with a sense of shame, and have to keep going so as to discover the mistakes. If we keep discovering mistakes and correcting them, then we may gradually improve ourselves. Chan practice requires us to use the methods of practice to examine our mind, which is the most important. Don''t be afraid of making mistakes; be afraid only of not recognizing mistakes. Don''t be afraid of having bad thoughts; be afraid only of being unaware of having bad thoughts.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('eYlIqjDPO18', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGPsFu6BDYVCuj9zqq1Kzdn', 'Pure mind is pure land(GDD-339, Master Sheng Yen)', 'A quiet mind isn''t necessarily a pure mind, and a tranquil land isn''t necessarily a pure land. Purity means when there is no vexation in the mind, and that when one has a wise mind not subject to any outside influence. We need to practice to avoid having a greedy mind, a hateful mind, a mind that is deluded, prideful, jealous, or doubting. When these negative mentalities are thoroughly cleaned up, one is pure in mind. Once your mind is pure, then the world you see is also pure—a pure land on earth.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('CmN7UdLDZdU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGPsFu6BDYVCuj9zqq1Kzdn', 'Buddhists'' patriotism(GDD-340, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Shakyamuni Buddha''s teachings, his views, and his methods actually aim to help people actively participate in the world, save the world and transform the world. Life involves birth, aging, sickness and death, which are all things Shakyamuni Buddha and Buddhists care a great deal about. The Buddha taught the Dharma in hope that we would use it to help ourselves, to adjust our attitude and perspective, and then help purify our society. Buddhists are never passive and negative.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('-VJ8PvyUkeU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGPsFu6BDYVCuj9zqq1Kzdn', 'How to get along with our co-workers(GDD-341, Master Sheng Yen)', 'From the perspective of the Buddhadharma, no matter what environment or situation we''re in, relationships between people should be open and harmonious. Harmony at the office depends on the system at work, and also on staff members'' attitude in getting along with each other. We should avoid making comparison with others, never mind what others do or what they think of us, and simply devote ourselves to our work wholeheartedly.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('0pqQWgTrk9o', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGPsFu6BDYVCuj9zqq1Kzdn', 'How do managers maintain a good relationship with their subordinates?(GDD-342, Master Sheng Yen)', 'A good mid-level manager is the one who does the planning for the boss. He devises strategies, does research, implements plans, and then divides and delegates the work carefully. After that he must coordinate and harmonize the lateral relations of the departments, and provide a working system for the company''s hierarchy. He solves all problems and is caring toward everyone, all the employees.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('A76fxgEFvFw', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGPsFu6BDYVCuj9zqq1Kzdn', 'What makes a great master?(GDD-348, Master Sheng Yen)', 'In Shakyamuni Buddha''s time, the title \"great master\" actually referred to the Buddha himself. During the course of history, calling someone a great master is a way for later generations to show their reverence for former masters, or it''s a way for disciples to address their highest mentor or leader, their spiritual leader. People are called a great master for a reason: They are broad-minded, visionary, charismatic, and inspire respect. They perform great meritorious deeds and possess great virtue and wisdom.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('9aP7aexMJ9A', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGPsFu6BDYVCuj9zqq1Kzdn', 'Why onions, garlic and leeks are seen as \"non-vegetarian\" foods(GDD-349, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism teaches that it''s best to refrain from eating the five pungent spices. There are two reasons for this: when you''re chanting sutras or when you''re receiving guests, it is impolite and disrespectful if your breath smells bad. The other reason is that they arouse anger when eaten raw; when eaten raw before they''re cooked, they make you irritable and ill-tempered. When eaten cooked, they arouse your passions; when you eat them cooked, they arouse your sexual desire and stimulate your sex drive.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('_tSWEv8bBkA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGPsFu6BDYVCuj9zqq1Kzdn', 'What kind of attitude should a business leader have(GDD-392, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The relationship between labor and management is interdependent, in which they interact with, help, need, and make demands of each other. Business owners, management and executives contribute a lot by investing capital, offering their wisdom and their time, and taking on risks, while employees put in their contributions through their hard work, cooperation, and support. This reflects the Buddhist teaching that every phenomenon, every achievement or success is the working together of many causes and conditions.');
INSERT INTO playlist(pid, cid, title, description) VALUES('PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h','UCBIGwiecylJsQrhTPBKI4Qw', 'GDD(0301-0325)', '');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('aSY__1NTDH8', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'How to cultivate the ability to be self-restrained and at peace(GDD-0312, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Idle people are unable to be at peace because their mind and body wander about, unable to settle down. We need to devote our body and mind to work, which can help put our body and mind at peace. We can only grow after we have worked hard; only after we have grown can we bring peace to ourselves and others.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('jZKAgei2t5k', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'The true meaning of happiness (GDD-0313, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Whether one can live in peace and happiness has mainly to do with one''s state of mind. Happiness is to be content and always joyful; happiness is to live fully in the present moment, to be mindful of our conduct and actions, and to face our own conscience truthfully; happiness is to count our karmic blessings and cultivate merit at all times.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('idQtOyAC7WE', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'How to adjust our disposition (GDD-0314, Master Sheng Yen)', 'We can adjust our mind as a way to help our physical health. We need to realize that birth, aging, sickness, and death are a natural part of our life, that to have some illness can motivate us to practice and achieve the Way, and that by falling sick we are actually paying off our karmic debts and therefore can feel carefree afterwards.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('4R4xDTYIy2A', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'Life''s responsibilities (GDD-0315, Master Sheng Yen)', 'From the Buddhist perspective, there are only two kinds of responsibility in life. The first is to fulfill our vows, and the second is to pay back our karmic debts. We should learn the Buddhas and bodhisattvas in making great vows to save suffering sentient beings. In paying back our karmic debts, we should actively contribute to our society for the benefit of the public, and treat any situation we encounter, whether good or bad, with equanimity.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('HpxHdf71XXg', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'Becoming a monastic and returning to lay life (GDD-0317, Master Sheng Yen)', 'There is nothing wrong with returning to lay life once becoming a Buddhist monk. If after making a sincere effort one finds that one''s habits and mindset are not suited to monasticism, one can still be a good lay practitioner.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('YSvlrUf56WU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'Male chauvinism (GDD-0318, Master Sheng Yen)', 'From the Buddhist perspective, men and women are equal because we can see in the sutras that Shakyamuni Buddha''s disciples included both men and women. Men can achieve the fruit of arhatship and so can women. It''s problematic for people to hold a double standard, being male chauvinistic themselves while expecting their own daughter to be treated with respect. People should treat women equally as they would like their daughter to be treated.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('f2E2sHpz8nE', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'What kind of books Buddhists should read (GDD-0319, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Although Buddhists are detached from worldly pursuits, that doesn''t mean they don''t care about the world. In order to care about people and the world, we need to understand and learn more about the people, affairs and things of the world. So Buddhists also need to read secular books; the Buddhadharma is actually not separate from the world. By combining Buddhism and secular learning, we can actually help ourselves and others better solve the problems in the world.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('aWfWQHFsuLs', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'Agricultural pollution (GDD-0320, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Using pesticides not only takes the life of those insects, but also kills people indirectly by contaminating the vegetables and fruit, as well as the soil. We can use natural or organic fertilizers, adopt indoor or greenhouse cultivation, and, if people believe in Buddhism, recite the Buddha''s name for those insects, wishing them to relocate or be reborn in the Western World of Ultimate Bliss.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('aVgvn_QTn_k', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'Bringing modern Buddhist music to greater heights(GDD-0301, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhist music can free our mind of desires and impurities and make us calm and composed. It can positively affect our lives with harmonious melodies, and help purify people''s minds and society.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('e_O_T5HWCg0', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'Appropriate ways of giving(GDD-0302, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Through the action of giving we foster our compassion and generosity, which will help us reduce our attachment and clinging to the self, and reduce the greed, craving, and desire of the self. Though the merit of giving may be subjective, we should do investigation and contribute to credible people and organizations, or to those who are truly sincere and deserve our support.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('zHWaqLz6NTA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'True filial piety(GDD-0303, Master Sheng Yen)', 'From a Buddhist point of view, filial piety really means that we support our parents, take care of their daily lives, their health and medical care, and even their religious and spiritual needs. Moreover, we should always be grateful for our parents'' loving concern, although we don''t necessarily need to stick to our parents'' ways, as times and society may have changed.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('rznkHXrNbiA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'How to break down the barriers of our mind(GDD-0304, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The barriers of our mind come from our five mental afflictions: greed, aversion, ignorance, arrogance and doubt. If we can transform the five mental afflictions into the mind of cultivation by being sincere and maintaining a warm and caring attitude, respecting people and treating them with dignity, concern, understanding and compassion rather than seeing others as enemies, then we wouldn''t need our mental defenses.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('OTdNuaTfp0c', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'How to cultivate patience(GDD-0305, Master Sheng Yen)', 'To develop our patience, whether it''s dealing with our job or with our relationships, first we must feel that the job is one we should do, we enjoy, and one we must complete. Secondly, we must realize that since we have no way to escape from someone or something we are supposed to deal with, we cannot but try to have patience.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('U3JfK4b18KU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'The Buddha saves those with affinities(GDD-0306, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The Buddha works to deliver all sentient beings in the hope that they may be delivered. But some people have heavy karmic hindrances, karmic retributions, and afflictive hindrances that keep them from believing in the Buddha or understanding the Buddhadharma in the right way. Nevertheless, the Buddhas and bodhisattvas will all actively teach the Dharma and deliver sentient beings by forever creating affinities and causing them to ripen.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Dum-Au9ucwU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'How to cultivate people with foresight(GDD-0307, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Our ingrained habits and our ways of thinking due to our self-centeredness have caused most of us to lack wisdom and compassion. By practicing the six perfections of the bodhisattva path—giving, keeping precepts, patience, diligence, concentration, and wisdom—we can transform ourselves to have more wisdom and compassion, and become a person with intelligence, foresight, and love.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('_Bi2nf5eWg8', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'How to cure the mind of those who''ve overindulged in ease and pleasure(GDD-0308, Master Sheng Yen)', 'We should be alert and vigilant even in times of peace and prosperity, always be prepared for impending disaster. So we must cultivate diligence and the ability to endure hardship, then whatever kind of environment or situation arises, we''ll be able to get through it safe and sound.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('qU43iJcFDk4', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'How to cultivate perseverance(GDD-0309, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Spiritual cultivation requires us to develop aspirations as a long-term, lasting goal. By setting an unchanging, ultimate goal we are then able to walk along our path, and move one step at a time, without losing our hope and giving up when encountering defeat or setbacks.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('YcRBCsPrJbg', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'How to keep our mental balance and relieve pressure in stressful times(GDD-0310, Master Sheng Yen)', 'When we feel pressure or stress, it means we have certain fears or we''re not feeling confident; we doubt our own capability so we feel we can''t shoulder the burden and wish we didn''t have to deal with it. We should try to use the slightest effort to deal with our problems by first understanding them very well, and manage to accomplish our task. When we''re doing a task, do not feel overwhelmed. Just put forth our best effort; there''s no need to worry about not doing it well.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('yx43W16Bbh8', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', '\"Are Buddhism''s buddha-nature and Confucianism''s idea of  inherent goodness .....?(GDD-0324)', '');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('CJnkg_eHALk', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'Is it possible to combine religions?(GDD-321, Master Sheng Yen) )', '');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('j7nuimiaWQA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'How to break through dichotomous thinking(GDD-322, Master Sheng Yen)', 'While dichotomous thinking is necessary for human culture and civilization, there must be communication and harmony between oppositions and contradictions in order to reach unity. After achieving unity, we must transcend it. Only then can we reach wisdom and absolute compassion, thereby attaining liberation and freedom.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('gXbkMokR1as', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrEJZSut8EvhkBDOiaVQl16h', 'Cultivating outstanding Buddhist talent(GDD-323, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The most talented and gifted sages in Buddhism are \"naturals.\" They aren''t a product of their environment or of education, but are a natural phenomenon. However, people with slightly lesser or average gifts, either monastics or lay practitioners, can still become Buddhist talent through formal Buddhist education, or through regular practice and study of Buddhist concepts and methods, being a driving force in the transformation of the world today.');
INSERT INTO playlist(pid, cid, title, description) VALUES('PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5','UCBIGwiecylJsQrhTPBKI4Qw', 'GDD(0276-0300)', '');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('DKLWiLZs6v8', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', '\"The mind changes with the environment\"(GDD-0291, Master Sheng Yen)', 'If our minds are affected by our environment, then we''ll change in accordance with it, feeling unstable and insecure. If we can keep our mind unaffected by our environment, then we won''t change with it no matter how our environment changes, and therefore remain composed and calm.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('1_sha3uo-Yg', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'Are bodhisattvas and Buddhas humans or deities?(GDD-0279, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Buddhas and bodhisattvas have the qualities of deities, such as the power to manifest spiritual responses, but Buddhas and bodhisattvas are sages who have only wisdom and compassion and are not attached to the self, and who have already achieved liberation, free from the afflictions of self-centeredness. \n\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('w_dqxeD7fP0', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'Buddhist education for children(GDD-0284, Master Sheng Yen)', 'It is essential for people to acquire their moral training and sense of ethics through inculcation from a very early age. Parents should make their child learn about and understand a religious faith that helps develop their gratitude, thankfulness, compassion, and wisdom, so that they grow up to be honest and upright people, kind and genuinely willing to help others.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('F1ZAf7D_T2Q', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'Does burning ghost money work?(GDD-0280, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Burning ghost money is not a part of Buddhist culture, nor is it a Buddhist belief. This is a part of Chinese culture that has more of a comforting effect rather than any substantial use for the dead. Therefore, Buddhism advocates reciting the Buddha''s name, preaching the Dharma or reciting the sutras for the deceased, to enable them to become detached, let go of the suffering, and be reborn in the Buddha''s Pure Land.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('OtPgTsqHzUI', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'How can we absorb the favorable elements of the West  culture?(GDD-0286, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The good point about Western culture is that it stresses straightforwardness and immediate results; it is good at material and technological cultures. While spiritual culture, or the culture of the inner life, is strength of Asia. We should be able to achieve a blend of the two; the two must be made to complement each other so they can work in harmony without contradiction.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('FRKfFGHzMpk', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'How to get teenagers to change their ways?(GDD-0283, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Our society has created an environment to encourage young people to look for stimulation and excitement instead of seeking true satisfaction and contentment. Parents should take responsibility for advising and educating their children from a young age about how to play in a way that is meaningful and is good for the mind and body. Business people must have morality and shouldn''t pander to the public with advertising lines that will cause damage to young people''s minds.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('KvhTc3G6E6Q', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'How to overcome deluded thoughts(GDD-0282, Master Sheng Yen)', 'It would be impossible for most people not to have wandering thoughts. It is fine as long as we recognize and be aware of our wandering thoughts. With spiritual practice, such as repentance prostration, reciting sutras or the Buddha''s name or mantras, and sitting meditation, we can train ourselves to calm and purify our minds, and thereby naturally reducing our distracting or wandering thoughts.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('1g8g9H7uTJs', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'How we can beyet happy, and tired but joyful(GDD-0290, Master Sheng Yen)', 'We have to be busy in that we need to use our limited lives and precious time to build up our wisdom and merit, by giving of ourselves to serve, help, and take care of others. In Buddhism, we''re busy for ourselves, so even if we''ve gotten nothing in this life, we''ll still have gained merit and the benefit of wisdom. Therefore, we''ll feel tired but very happy for having the opportunity to be busy.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('enzxTlig1l0', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'Pursuing a perfect character(GDD-0289, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Pursuit of perfection is impractical, for our wisdom has its limitations and we are bound to have many blind spots, plus the fact that our self-understanding is incomplete. Perfection in its true sense means when our mind isn''t perturbed by the environment because of our confidence and wisdom, while being sincere and genuine, admitting it when we are wrong and continuing our efforts to make progress and improve ourselves.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('r04fmwK7rlw', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'The meaning of \"giver of joy\"(GDD-0287, Master Sheng Yen)', 'At Dharma Drum Mountain, managers are referred to as the \"giver of joy\" in the hope that those in the managerial position can, based on the Buddhist idea that all sentient beings are equal and have the Buddha-nature, use their ability and intelligence to serve others and help others to grow, so that everyone feels peaceful and happy.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('pXUS0UyLCP8', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'What to do if you accidentally eat meat while practicing vegetarianism(GDD-0288, Master Sheng Yen)', 'A full vegetarian must have a firm will and confidence in themselves to stick to vegetarianism, while following Buddhism in a natural and easy manner without making things difficult for themselves or become imprisoned by their own inflexible views.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('KYAnJMuGBTo', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'Why do we often address others as \"bodhisattva?\"(GDD-0277, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"A bodhisattva is someone who hasn''t achieved Buddhahood yet but wants to become a Buddha. Anybody who''s walking on the path towards Buddhahood is called a bodhisattva. As a bodhisattva with initial aspiration to the Way we may still be afflicted by vexations and also experience suffering, but we can practice being wise and compassionate, then our mind will be tranquil and peaceful and we will have fewer vexations.\n\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('ElSJBXCDzr8', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'What''s DDM''s goal in activities?(GDD-0293, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Dharma Drum Mountain seeks to address the problems of our day by promoting its vision of uplifting the character of humanity and building a pure land on earth based on the spiritual environmentalism campaign, which has received much of a response from its own followers, other Buddhist groups, and society.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('ShDEHnUTofU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'How can we achieve the right balance between contending and not contending', 'To achieve the right balance between contending and not contending, as well as giving and receiving, Buddhists should make a proper judgment between whether it is for the sake of personal interest or for sentient beings and Buddhism as a whole.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('jcr0GS5h5oM', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'Outlook of the 21st century(GDD-0295, Master Sheng Yen)', 'As technology continues to develop and become more and more advanced, our material standard of living will become better and better, but the damage to our environment and the loss and waste of our natural resources will grow more serious, and the feeling of emptiness will grow stronger. In the future people will need religion; we will need the Buddhadharma to offer us a guidance to be at peace, and a way to think about and deal with interpersonal relationships.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('bKAkXVIZtJE', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'How to calm an agitated mind(GDD-0296, Master Sheng Yen)', 'If there''s a problem anywhere on this planet, other places will also experience related problems. First of all, we have to face reality and acknowledge that the real world is unstable. Secondly, it''s very important to train ourselves to have peace of mind; once our mind is tranquil and calm, no matter how chaotic the environment is or how it changes, our mind will still be able to stay calm and collected.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('5NYxVnCPC2k', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'How to encourage people to practice Buddhism (GDD-0297, Master Sheng Yen)', 'To help Buddhist practitioners persevere in their practice and not give up, monasteries can train more monastics to offer care and concern activities for their devotees. Buddhist followers, when first taking up Buddhism, should take their vows seriously enough, develop the bodhi-mind, and resolve to follow the bodhisattva path. Lay practitioners can take turns organizing group practice activities in their homes, encouraging and helping each other to continue treading the way to bodhi');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('kmHwoa7zob8', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'Easy methods for calming our body and mind(GDD-0298, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism incorporates a variety of practices to help us calm our body and mind, and it all depends on whether we do these practices on a regular basis. In our daily lives, we can spare a certain period of time for regular practice, or, when we don''t need to use our brains, recite the Buddha''s name, and use Buddhist views to calm our mind.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('fWWWGe1WUj4', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'How should we view the dreams we have of our dead relatives or friends?(GDD-0299, Master Sheng Yen)', 'When we have dreams of our deceased loved ones, the best thing that we can do for them is to recite the Buddha''s name or the sutras and transfer the merit to them. This is the best way to help.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('pnjHjGZDGxg', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'How should Buddhists take care of their appearance ?(GDD-0300, Master Sheng Yen)', 'While excessive adornment is unnecessary, we should take care of our appearance in an appropriate manner, partly to ensure a hygienic environment and to show respect and courtesy to others, and partly to establish an image as a means for helping sentient beings.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('HjjsGvFbp-w', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrFYz6n1-1hV9xGfUDwSRdD5', 'How to properly dispose of old and used things(GDD-0292, Master Sheng Yen)', 'For economic and aesthetic reasons it may make sense to replace old things with new ones, but this does a lot of damage to our natural environment. Of the goods in our everyday life we need to tell the difference between basic necessities and luxury items. The government, as well as industry and commerce, should spend money on researching a set of methods that not only allows for the collection of used plastic products, but also enables them to be recycled and reused again and again.');
INSERT INTO playlist(pid, cid, title, description) VALUES('PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U','UCBIGwiecylJsQrhTPBKI4Qw', 'GDD(0251-0275)', '');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('5F9gbRQgVOs', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'How to avoid falsehood(GDD-0251, Master Sheng Yen)', 'To speak falsehood is to speak words or speak in a way that harms or hurts people and affects people negatively. Although sometimes there is a need for funny, lighthearted remarks to cheer people up, it is always a best policy to be compassionate and sincere in what we say, in order to get somebody''s respect, earn somebody''s trust, or make people feel we''re amiable and trustworthy.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('qhaGeW1ZHbY', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'How to find a suitable job(GDD-0252, Master Sheng Yen)', 'There is no perfect job in the world. Some people are unsure about what job would suit them best mainly because they don''t understand themselves or lack a clear direction in life. Young people should take their first job as an opportunity to train their patience and perseverance, which will eventually help them earn a steady job.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('bhKqgvi4EFg', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'How to deal with setbacks(GDD-0253, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Dreams and goals are not the same; young people often take their dreams for goals. While it is necessary to have hope, plans, and also dreams for the future, when our dreams are not realized, we must still have peace of mind and not feel troubled, for we have gained wisdom and experience.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('_NzU2mGqNj0', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'Parents with teenage children(GDD-0256, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Our times may have changed and the ideas about educating children may have changed with the times, but what remains true is that family atmosphere affects the personality of the children and their psychological health. At home, parents should be kind and good-natured, if their opinions differ they must communicate and act for the welfare of the child. If the parents are kind and loving, the child will feel secure. \n\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('1tMbFoPJyDA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'What attitude should young people have towards the opposite sex?(GDD-0257, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Promiscuity is an irresponsible act towards others, oneself, other people''s families, and society as a whole; it can cause troublesome issues that lead to family problems and also cause problems in educating the children. We must strive to teach our children basic values and beliefs, preferably in some kind of religious belief, so that they can grow up with the relevant moral discipline and restraint.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('C0DMkTlV7jA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'How do Buddhist summer camps benefit young people?(GDD-0258, Master Sheng Yen)', 'We organize Buddhist summer camps to offer children help and guidance through environmental influences on two levels. First, through group activities and very relaxed courses, we teach them basic Buddhist ideas that one should care for and help others. Secondly, we design spiritual activities such as prostrating to the Buddha, seated meditation, and reciting the Buddha''s name.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('BSyiN3-tEy4', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'Buddhist songs for children(GDD-0259, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Music can express emotions and feelings that language cannot. Buddhist children''s songs are a good way to present the teachings and spirit of Buddhism in a simple and easy to understand way that is also interesting and enjoyable to children.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('glhF92DqGw8', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'Integration of various methods of Buddhist practice(GDD-0260, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Integration of various methods of Buddhist practice cannot be done and is not necessary, in that people''s preferences and aptitudes are not the same. The ideal way is to know how to choose a Dharma gate that is most suitable. Whatever we are learning or want to learn, once we have started and feel that it is good, then keep on learning it.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('s9zte2ZllYY', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'Teen crimes(GDD-0261, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The problem of teen crimes can be attributed mostly to the state of our society as a whole. If we can care more for children, both our own children and other people''s children,  and if parents can spend more time with their children and show more understanding for them, they will more likely become good children.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('uxxV3yZe6Xo', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'Will eating a vegetarian diet lead to malnutrition for children?(GDD-0262, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Nowadays, not everyone is vegetarian for religious reasons. Some are vegetarians for reasons of health, and some because they care for animals. Some people are vegetarians from childhood, but their bodies don''t lack anything. When our body needs something, it will take the food we have eaten and change it into whatever our body needs. As long as one is not a picky eater, one shouldn''t worry that vegetarianism means poor nutrition.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('KGJsPHTwnO0', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'Déjà vu(GDD-0263, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"There are several kinds of dreaming: the kind in which something appears in someone''s dreams because it is frequently on their mind; the kind in which something we may never have thought of or seen appears in our dreams due to the activity of our consciousness; the kind to do with one''s spiritual response with a deity or spirit; and the kind as a result of one''s own power of spiritual practice.\n\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('YvwaXz2q7JU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'How to address Buddhist clerics(GDD-0264, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Master,\" \"venerable master\" and \"Dharma master\" are all polite forms of address for Buddhist monks. It is improper to use overly respectful titles like \"great master,\" an honorific title for the Buddha, for ordinary monastics.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('W9lv6ryGNsg', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'Is it right to travel far from your parents when they''re still alive?(GDD-0265, Master Sheng Yen)', 'In our commercial and industrial society we may not be able to take care of our parents in the same way as people did in ancient, agricultural society by living with our parents, we should still show concern for them and provide for their care in a thorough manner.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Uw45wHo4D7c', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'Why we should eat a vegetarian breakfast on a regular basis(GDD-0266, Master Sheng Yen)', 'To abstain from eating meat on certain meals or certain days as a practice is a good way to practice living a simple life with fewer desires and cultivate our compassion, thereby improving our fate, our society, and environment.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('dkzEZ_57XUw', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'Why there are so many Buddhas, bodhisattvas and deities in Buddhism(GDD-0267, Master Sheng Yen)', 'There are many Buddhas in the past, present, and future; Buddhahood is achieved by sentient beings. A bodhisattva is one who is in the process of going from the stage of sentient being to Buddhahood. Bodhisattvas help Buddhas and work with Buddhas to deliver sentient beings. Deities protect the Three Jewels—the Buddha, the Dharma and the Sangha—so that the Buddhadharma may be propagated smoothly and numerous beings may be delivered. That is why in monasteries of Mahayana Buddhism there are many statues of Buddhas, bodhisattvas, and deities.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('j7OWfCpfpXg', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'Why do some people refer to influential Buddhist groups as shantou, or \"factions\"?(GDD-0268)', '\"Indian Buddhism was split into twenty schools after Shakyamuni Buddha''s death due to the fact that different places with different customs, different conventions, and different needs required that the application and interpretation of the Dharma be carried out from different viewpoints. Similarly, within the Buddhist community nowadays, different big monasteries or organizations may be using different means or methods to do their own things, but they share the same basic ideals and principles as Buddhist groups.\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('k-3hbB5LW6I', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'How funeral arrangements should be handled if there are different religious beliefs in a family(269)', 'In holding funerals, family members should show respect for their parents'' faith. If the other family members aren''t clear about their own faith or that of the deceased, then we Buddhists may take the initiative and advise them to hold a Buddhist funeral. Yet if they insist on their individual preferences, then it''s advisable to use different rites as preferred, while Buddhist family members should hold their own delivery or prayer service for the deceased.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('suiKUY6qrEA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'Do Buddhists attach importance to celebrating birthdays?(GDD-0270, Master Sheng Yen)', 'If we live in this world with the best intentions, do good deeds, are righteous and generous with people, and help others as much as we can, then that is the best way to celebrate our own birthdays. The true meaning to celebrate parents'' birthdays is to make their lives happier and make them feel at peace by taking care of them with respect and devotion, and by being a kind and good person.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('a3OAjOMMQfE', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'Why does everyone want to get married in a church and not at a Buddhist temple?(GDD-0271)', 'People like to have weddings in churches because they are simple, impressive and solemn. This type of atmosphere gives the couple a feeling of dignity. So as Buddhist monastics interact with lay people every day, it is necessary to design and organize impressive, solemn, and simple humanized Buddhist marriage ceremonies, to let the couple feel that they have grown, their sense of responsibility has increased, and their character has grown.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('L4LxVU8hzwM', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'The surnames of monastics(GDD-0272, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhist monks in China all use the surname Shi derived from Shakya—Shakyamuni Buddha''s clan name—which shows that they are children of Shakyamuni Buddha. We should only ask monastics their Dharma name, not their surname.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('6uiZDo1p2ns', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', 'Why is the Land of Utmost Bliss in the west?(GDD-0274, Master Sheng Yen)', 'According to the sutras, there are innumerable Buddhas in the ten directions of the universe. The reason why Shakyamuni Buddha introduced Amitabha Buddha''s Pure Land to us is that with the power of Amitabha Buddha''s vows people who have firm faith in the Pure Land can be reborn there, where there are no obstacles for one''s practice of the Buddha path and therefore one can achieve Buddhahood quickly and then return to this Saha World or go to other worlds to liberate sentient beings.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('tPOjisT5REs', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE2f9ShuxPhQ-iVnmA_Et6U', '(GDD-0275, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism teaches people to develop a peaceful and positive mindset with wisdom, compassion, so as to stay unaffected by external unrest and chaos. While those who truly practice the Dharma and help others to practice are too small in number, we should still make a great effort to promote Buddhism, which is of wisdom and compassion and offers stability and a sense of security, and thereby making our society more peaceful and harmonious.');
INSERT INTO playlist(pid, cid, title, description) VALUES('PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg','UCBIGwiecylJsQrhTPBKI4Qw', 'GDD(0226-0250)', '');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('mZWTdDAYgGI', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'Religious literature and Buddhist books(GDD-0226, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Although all the religious literature out there promotes respect for morality and encourages people to do good, wholesome deeds, Buddhist books, including the Buddhist cannon, have much more to offer in that they are all-embracing, all-inclusive, and all-transcending.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Er3b2wl62WY', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'What should we do to curb cruel forms of entertainment?(GDD-0227, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Cruelty sports and fighting games should not be encouraged because they pollute our kindness and compassion, the best parts of our humanity, and have a bad effect on children''s psychological maturation. Since we hope that everyone will be able to live together in peace and harmony, we should respect and love each other by starting from our inner peace and not having cruelty in our hearts.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('2zbg3W1RXH0', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'Protecting wildlife(GDD-0228, Master Sheng Yen)', 'As cause and effect relationships operate in nature, the more we destroy natural ecology, the greater the price we will have to pay. From a Buddhist point of view, sentient beings are all equal. Numerous sentient beings live with us in the same world; just as human beings want to survive, we should respect the right of all wildlife to live as long as it does not threaten our life.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('vbnD_Sboglo', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'Vegetarianism(GDD-0229, Master Sheng Yen)', 'People practice vegetarianism for health concerns or religious reasons. Practicing vegetarianism enables people to have a gentler and friendlier temperament, a more peaceful aura, good health, and relatively pure blood.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('xEg4_yxfZx8', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'How to cultivate Buddhist talent(GDD-0230, Master Sheng Yen)', 'To serve society and humanity as a whole, the Buddhist circles should nurture talent that can not only organize and lead religious activities, but also give a lecture on Buddhism. More challenging is to cultivate talent to be Dharma teachers or Chan masters. Also required is to train Buddhist monastics in different ways in order that they can fulfill tasks in different fields, including social services and education.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Tj1TfGsY8NM', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'How Buddhism can serve as a compass for the times(GDD-0231, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhist methods and forms must change according to the times and the environment, in order to maintain its principle of enabling people to obtain wisdom and thus to cut off their own afflictions, as well as to obtain compassion and thus to help others resolve their problems and free themselves from suffering.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('INzBpt3feVQ', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'Buddhism for the young generation(GDD-0232, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism is gradually gaining acceptance among the younger generation because it fulfills those who are thoughtful and contemplative in their spiritual quests. Also, Buddhism has a wide range of philosophical theories and practice methods to offer people with different educational levels and cultural backgrounds.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('R0Yoaf2vPcM', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'Should monastics stick to practicing asceticism ？(GDD-0233, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Although the Buddha encourages the ascetic practices of Buddhist monks, ascetic monks must go beg for alms among people, interacting with people and preaching the Dharma. In order for Buddhism to widely and deeply interact with people and merge into society, Buddhist practitioners should often be present in every corner of society.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('LeKf3vymcNc', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'What''s the correct attitude for studying Buddhism?(GDD-0234, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Correct attitude for studying Buddhism involves using the right methods of practice and having a good grasp of the essentials. Enlightenment means to let go of self-centeredness, discrimination, craving, and desire; it means detachment and freedom of body and mind and letting go of the surrounding environment or world.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('I8XfheH56dI', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'The importance of focusing deeply on one method(GDD-0235, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism emphasizes that in spiritual practice one should focus deeply on one method, be engaged in it, and practice it as best one can. Only when we have achieved sufficient mastery of one method can we then move on to something else. Otherwise we will end up getting confused and achieving nothing.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('L3xzWBeKZj8', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'Cherishing blessings(GDD-0236, Master Sheng Yen)', 'We are closely related to the people of ancient times, to the people in the world today, and to the people of the future; all sentient beings share a common fate. By wasting natural resources we are not only exhausting our blessings but also destroying the natural environment for our future generations; by cherishing our blessings we are actually saving them for the future.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('PYQG-Sthu5Y', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'Avoid all that is evil, do all that is good(GDD-0237, Master Sheng Yen)', 'While Buddhism encourages people to abstain from evil and do good deeds, its main aim is to teach people to purify their own minds. If our mind is impure, we are liable to use impure speech and perform impure physical acts at anytime. We should purify our mind by constantly remaining aware of, repenting of, and cleaning the impure thoughts in our mind.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('3SpLGsBhaiU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'How can we practice the Way with perseverance?(GDD-0238, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Just as the reality that anyone who wants to achieve something significant must have patience and perseverance, we must exercise patience and work hard non-stop in our practice of the Buddha path. Though we may not be able to see immediate results, we are actually growing and making progress every day.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('76IhrSc1HE0', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'The importance of shame and repentance(GDD-0239, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Shame and repentance go together and complement each other. With a sense of shame, we are able to admit our faulty behaviors. Repentance means taking responsibility for our faults. By having the sense of shame and repenting, we show our willingness to shoulder responsibility and are determined not to repeat the same mistake, and thereby eradicating our karmic hindrances.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('dqqbmMx8t7E', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'How to make our progress along the path of cultivation(GDD-0240, Master Sheng Yen)', 'When we encounter adversity in our spiritual practice, we shouldn''t always suppose it is a demon, but should take it as a kind of training, something we inevitably have to go through when we are making progress. Most of the time, the demonic state reflects the demons of our own mind, such as when we have imaginary fears due to suspicion or when we want to get something for nothing.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('cJweA-X-x1k', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'How to set up a Buddhist altar at home(GDD-0241, Master Sheng Yen)', 'From the Buddhist perspective, the question of having an altar at home or not is not a problem. If there is enough room in the house and the conditions allow then it''s very good to have a altar or shrine. Most importantly is to have an image of the Buddha in our mind, keep the Buddha in our mind and act in line with the Buddha''s teachings.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('xmMLEosu7Zo', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'Taking refuge(GDD-0242, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Taking refuge means to identify with, accept and depend upon the Three Jewels—the Buddha, the Dharma and the Sangha. By taking refuge in the Three Jewels we are affirming and declaring ourselves a Buddhist, and making a vow to follow Buddhism, using the Buddhist concepts and methods to guide us and help us to progress along the bodhisattva path.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('cNjg1ca59Xw', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'How can young people help themselves and make their contribution?(GDD-0243, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Young people may feel worried or panic-stricken when first entering the job market, which is like entering a new world. Entering this new stage of life, new graduates should mentally prepare themselves and not set their ideals too high. The priority consideration is to find a job, one we can live on and gain our foothold in and make a contribution in, with which we can gradually work towards the future.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('nGOGBtjOw14', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'How should we help young people to embrace good values?(GDD-0244, Master Sheng Yen)', 'When we seek personal gain and interest, we must think beyond ourselves and consider the benefits of others. In Buddhism we should encourage young people to understand the purpose and value of human existence, and to use wisdom and hard work to make contributions to society and take making a contribution as their goal and value of life.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('PNP-6hBopWA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'How do we instill proper religious views in young people?(GDD-0245, Master Sheng Yen)', 'To help children and young people truly know Buddhism, we must begin with the parents. At home parents can encourage children to worship the Buddha, recite Amitabha Buddha''s name or the Bodhisattva''s name (Avalokitesvara or Ksitigarbha), and tell them that the purpose is to seek wisdom and compassion. Monasteries can help in this respect by providing children''s class.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('L8GNg-Q9t4M', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'How we can learn to achieve the carefree ease of \"non-striving\"(GDD-0247, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Although competing and striving is an ingrained habit of humans, what makes us humans truly human is the fact that we have wisdom, rationality, and feelings, and can always use education to transform our habits and character. It''s very important to affirm our own value ourselves, no matter how much we can contribute, no matter how much we understand and whatever we have achieved. Being able to admit and face defeat or failure is also self-affirmation.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('z58ZC6olna8', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'How we may avoid becoming the slaves of our craving(GDD-0248, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The desire to satisfy our wants or excessive, superfluous demands is craving. After satisfying our basic needs to make a living, we should have a greater desire by having hope for everybody, for the everlasting good of a greater environment.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('8QXCLb5u2F4', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'How to become a contented person(GDD-0249, Master Sheng Yen)', 'True contentedness means that all those material things, worldly possessions, desires and cravings are no longer important to us. We should train ourselves to be content by having few desires, and live a more fulfilled life by using our wisdom and our physical strength to help other people and by making efforts to contribute to society.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('D8iIdjmHCEA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrG0yk_g0vOHZCwV0qT_1_Fg', 'How we can become unselfish(GDD-0250, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Smart selfishness is the kind that benefits oneself but also benefits others. The most reliable way to be \"selfish\" is to benefit oneself by benefiting others. In terms of bodhisattva practice, the primary goal is to benefit others; yet in the process as we benefit others, we also benefit themselves.');
INSERT INTO playlist(pid, cid, title, description) VALUES('PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM','UCBIGwiecylJsQrhTPBKI4Qw', 'GDD(0201-0225)', 'GDD(0201-0225)');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('51gAdq1TYis', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'Only well-measured practice is the middle way(GDD-0201, Master Sheng Yen)', 'In spiritual practice, we shouldn''t ask for too many results at a time, and we mustn''t work too hard or be too sluggish. For personal practice, we must deeply practice just one Dharma method, instead of trying to be adept at many things in one go. In fact, once we have successfully practiced one method, we will be able to penetrate all others.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('552LPVJIyNA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'How to carefully select a site for Dharma practice(GDD-0202, Master Sheng Yen)', 'When we first try to practice Buddhism, we have to overcome our mental obstacles by making a firm resolve. Then we need to spare time for practice by cutting back on not very important socializing, and by stopping idling away our time. Finally, choose a suitable Dharma practice center that teaches and practices the correct Buddhadharma.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('nz8w80BHvGQ', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'What constitutes a world religion(GDD-0203, Master Sheng Yen)', 'A world religion is a religion that is not only accepted by a large number of people, but can continue to be passed on through the ages of history; it is not just widespread, but can stand the test of time. A true world religion must remain everlastingly fresh and new, and be able to make adjustments in their ideas, forms or methods when time requires it.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('S5GQL6ru1kw', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'The difference between Mahayana and Hinayana Buddhism(GDD-0204, Master Sheng Yen)', 'In Shakyamuni Buddha''s time, Buddhism had not split into Mahayana and Hinayana, though Mahayana ideas were already circulating. The distinction between Mahayana and Hinayana and their later developments reflect the different ways of interpreting the Buddha''s ideas and the precepts. While Hinayana Buddhism is a conservative form of Buddhism that adheres to Pali scriptures and the Buddha''s original teachings, Mahayana Buddhism emphasizes the Bodhisattva spirit in delivering senting beings and transforming the world.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('YS-6PLv7a1w', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'Where exactly are the pure lands?(GDD-0205, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Although the idea of rebirth in Amitabha Buddha''s Pure Land is much encouraged in Shakyamuni Buddha''s teachings, the fundamental philosophy of pure land all comes down to the cultivation of a pure mind, a state of mind that is free of greed, hatred, and ignorance.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('jAQ4jjHqn8I', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'Why academics value Buddhism?(GDD-0206, Master Sheng Yen)', 'In Buddhism, theory and practice are supposed to join together, instead of turning Buddhism into an academic discipline without involving cultivation and faith. By simultaneously studying, practicing, and cultivating, we are more able to truly understand Buddhism, and truly discover the essence of Buddhism or what Buddhism''s advantages are.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('XoqnuqyEypA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'Giving up grasping(GDD-0207, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The mind of grasping is a mind that always looks outward and pursues things in the external world. Buddhism offers us methods to train ourselves to lessen such a mind, help us to concentrate our mind so that it becomes quiet and peaceful. By grasping less at external things, our mind won''t be so distracted and confused and therefore we can store up our mental and physical energy for meaningful work.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('b6hCvvbmCf4', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'How we can lead a life of abundance(GDD-0208, Master Sheng Yen)', 'After satisfying our basic needs for living, we should seek spiritual satisfaction. Religious satisfaction is a form of spiritual satisfaction that is relatively easy to achieve; as long as we have faith and actually practice accordingly we will feel that we are secure and our life is blessed with abundance. The most reliable satisfaction to obtain is when we give of ourselves to benefit others.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('nkpulCXuo9E', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'Karmic power and the unconscious(GDD-0209, Master Sheng Yen)', 'In terms of psychology, the unconscious is not something that we can control or are aware of, while karmic power, a Buddhist concept similar to the unconscious, is a kind of power produced by our actions in countless past lives, which we can change our karma by understanding its source and not letting it grow.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('ZDbyahJ6fIA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'Emptiness and psychodynamics(GDD-0210, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The consciousness-only theory in Buddhism is a study of psychological analysis, which analyzes the mind in great detail. Ego, in Buddhism, is a tendency to cling to an illusion and is constantly changing, and so it is a false or delusory self. Buddhism advocates no-self, a true self that is free of any kind of attachment and realizes emptiness, meaning neither existence nor non-existence.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Br9dMhvZDGM', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'Having few desires and being content (GDD-0211, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism teaches that life is suffering, including the suffering of not getting what one wants. The antidote is to have few desires beyond one''s own needs and be content with what one absolutely needs for daily use.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('X_4l1Byh4NU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'Mundane dharmas - worldly phenomena (GDD-0212, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism teaches that mundane and supramundane dharmas are one and the same. The Platform Sutra states, \"Buddhadharma is of this world, and is to be experienced without leaving it. To leave this world to seek enlightenment is like searching a rabbit for its horns.\" The world gives us a point toward which to apply our efforts, to practice living our lives without feeling distressed or afflicted. This is called transcending the world.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('cCt1EuMiPAA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'The Buddhist concept of karmic causality (GDD-0213, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism looks at the process of life in the context of the past, present, and future lives. For good and bad karma that was sown in the past, we will receive the karmic results in this present life or in future lives. By accepting this law of karmic causality, we can face reality bravely and willingly, and, additionally, maintain infinite hope for the future.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('toLu6Bn3TrM', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'The true meaning of the Buddhadharma (GDD-0214, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The Buddhadharma is not separated from mundane dharmas and all dharmas of the mundane world are the Buddhadharma. As long as we see through things and perceive them as empty, and are therefore not attached to them at all, then we can be free of the affliction and attain liberation from the sea of suffering.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('K2p95rWz3CE', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'The true meaning of one''s urge to climb higher (GDD-0215, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The urge to climb higher reflects a human instinct to survive and develop. We should combine this instinct with our spiritual dimension and go beyond, emulating the spirit of the bodhisattva and seeking growth by contributing ourselves.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('x7EMj2OUVJI', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'How we can avoid letting our ego get inflated (GDD-0216, Master Sheng Yen)', 'An inflated ego is illusory and impractical as personal successes are not achieved single-handedly, but are the result of a multitude of factors. We should constrain ourselves by thinking that even if we achieve something extraordinary that contributes to the whole nation or the whole world, it is actually brought about by the blessings arising from the merit of all sentient beings.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('BErZ_OYJhAQ', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'The difference between traditional and new religions (GDD-0217, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The formation of new religions is a very natural development in response to the needs of our time, the needs of modern people in a new environment. Although some new religions or religious sects may tend to think and act erroneously, they help spur traditional Buddhism to reform and modernize, while its basic principles remain unchanged.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('ZPKxedEfAPg', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'The importance of religious education (GDD-0218, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Religious education, in terms of nurturing qualified religious teachers, is important in that it ensures a religion''s development and its dissemination in a pure and orthodox form, and it also helps a religion to offer its services to society, contributing to the welfare of society.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('1-cz6q1x8TU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'Compassionate aid, culture and spiritual practice (GDD-0219, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The three areas of compassionate aid, cultural education, and spiritual practice are all necessary for Buddhism as a whole. Compassionate aid represents the practice of giving; cultural education nurtures talent to spread and share the message; and spiritual practice refines and elevates our spirit.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('bvTUasPluLg', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'Outer paths (GDD-0220, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Instead of referring to heresy, \"outer path\" means seeking spiritual or material assistance from a source outside oneself. Buddhism teaches about realizing the mind and seeing the nature from within because the fundamental Buddha nature lies in the mind. However, outer paths can always serve as a way through which one learns to let go of one''s original clinging mind.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('TeqTcOyw6rs', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'The importance of being able to identify true religious books (GDD-0221, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Though some occult sciences or folk religions do share a common basis with higher forms of religion, they lack the features, contents, and functions to be a religion. A Buddhist should solely rely on the Buddha, Dharma, and Sangha, and should not follow unorthodox cults or outer-path ways, which cannot give up clinging to the self and embrace the concepts of impermanence and no-self.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('C8W8zLOjb-k', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'Buddhist perspective on rights and equality (GDD-0222, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Regarding equality, the Buddha taught that all sentient beings possess the intrinsic wisdom of the Buddha, and that, in teaching his monastic disciples, when one was willing to leave the household life to practice the path one could become an arhat, whether one was a man or a woman. On the issue of shared rights, the Buddha taught that every person has the same human dignity and everybody is equal, although they may be receiving different education and are assigned different tasks.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('j9rBi8fxGyo', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'How Buddhists can both be engaged in the world and transcend it (GDD-0223, Master Sheng Yen)', 'One can be engaged in the world while transcending it regardless of one''s physical location. It all lies in whether one can serve society and help solve problems of the world while living a life that accords with the standards of the Dharma, without creating disorder and being possessive of worldly things and affairs.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('noNqCZVkBQk', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGn_7klo81RBDelnITrOgfM', 'Mystical experience (GDD-0224, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Mystical experiences may happen as a production of one''s personal spiritual cultivation or come from an external force. Mystical experiences can help develop one''s self-confidence and enhance one''s faith in one''s religion and teacher, on the premise that such powers or experiences are not violating the law of karmic causality.');
INSERT INTO playlist(pid, cid, title, description) VALUES('PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN','UCBIGwiecylJsQrhTPBKI4Qw', 'GDD(0176-0200)', 'GDD(0176-0200)');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('BfXOWJoc5Ak', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'Learning to let go in life(GDD-0176, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Human beings always hope for increase. Real addition means that, while one may be gaining more fame, status, power, and wealth, one should also grow in merit, wisdom, and compassion. Otherwise, it is like taking more and more money out of a bank account, with the account balance getting smaller and smaller.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Pqf-RHoHh5s', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'The true meaning of universal love(GDD-0177, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism encourages the kind of love for all humanity, for all sentient beings, or, in Buddhist terms, unconditioned compassion. As the Diamond Sutra teaches, \"\"Without dwelling in anything whatsoever, allow this mind to arise,\"\" one should help others without thought of helping others and expecting anything in return.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('YiYhUZX10gQ', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'The true meaning of a practical life(GDD-0178, Master Sheng Yen)', 'To live a practical life is to cherish our life in the here and now, treasuring the time and environment we have and using them wisely, such as reciting the Buddha''s name, doing good deeds, spreading the Buddhadharma, taking part in volunteer work, engaging in social service, and showing concern for people in general. While it is important to work when it''s time to work, we should also rest when it''s time to rest and relax when it''s time to relax.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('yYbvoGFS5m8', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'Realizing the value of  life(GDD-0179, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The value of life depends on how we use our lives. If what we want are positive values, we must use our bodily, verbal, and mental actions to achieve sufficient growth in our morals, character, and humanity.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('jpamHL0N2Mk', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'How to break through the stifling distress that engulfs our lives(GDD-0180, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Shakyamuni Buddha taught us that life is suffering. Buddhism is to resolve the suffering of our world by offering people with Buddhist concepts and methods to deal with and transform the suffering.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('_tXgeSYeQ5E', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'Following your conscience(GDD-0181, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Moral intuition or conscience often clashes with human desire. Because we are human beings and not animals, we have to safeguard our conscience and not to abandon it and nurture our desires. It takes practice to maintain a conscience and use our conscience to judge.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('bwDGfR3JKTE', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'Cultivating moral courage(GDD-0182, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The reckless courage of the ordinary people is just bravery that lacks wisdom, the courage of those who do not know themselves, while the moral courage taught in Buddhism is the kind that shoulders all the burdens that no one else can bear, with patience, perseverance, and a profound mind.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('UyrN6QGtwko', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'An untainted mind(GDD-0183, Master Sheng Yen)', 'From a Buddhist standpoint, we bring the contamination with us at birth due to our beginningless ignorance, so our mind may impulsively give rise to emotions and desires in any circumstance. We can just tell ourselves to calm down and relax our mind, making it less susceptible to external environment.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('5AcymJGbj2o', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'How to become more broadminded(GDD-0184, Master Sheng Yen)', 'To develop a broad mind, we can learn to regard time and space as everlasting and endless. With this breadth of mind, we will be able to let go of our ego, embrace and be more tolerant of all people and all situations, thereby attaining the sense of ease and freedom.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('OcqhqMlMiVw', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'A peaceful mind(GDD-0185, Master Sheng Yen)', 'A peaceful mind, or an \"ordinary mind\" in terms of Chan Buddhism, is the state of mind unaffected by external situations and therefore free of fluctuation or inner conflicts, while remaining clearly aware of whatever there is in our surroundings.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Ff9diishvT0', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'Taking control of our mind(GDD-0186, Master Sheng Yen)', 'When we don''t have a firm standpoint and a clear direction, we have no control of our own mind. By practicing spiritually, cultivating insight and concentration, we will know our direction and standpoint better and therefore become more aware and gain mastery of our own mind.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('1oDRJjDNJ98', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'How to realize non-self(GDD-0187, Master Sheng Yen)', 'To realize non-self, we must first let go of a foolish and selfish self that seeks temporary benefit and advantage for ourselves but causes others to suffer losses, and then practice  doing meritorious deeds without calculating whether we will gain any merit, and regard it as something we should do.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('JIyEKlM4h7M', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'Contemplating the impurities of the body(GDD-0188, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The practice of mindfulness of the body as impure is to help us eliminate our clinging to the self. Though our body is impure and unclean, it is a useful tool with which we can practice the way of bodhisattva, cultivating merit and wisdom. We still have to protect it and keep it healthy so it can serve its proper purposes.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('NAaPjJTJevE', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'Mindfulness of sensation as suffering(GDD-0189, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The practice of contemplating our sensation, or feelings, as suffering is to make us aware that in this world suffering is the rule, while joy is a temporary exception. By having fewer desires and being content, we can minimize our cravings for the pursuit of all kinds of desires, and eventually attain liberation, which is the eternal joy.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('dIRhNvaBhZk', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'Mindfulness of the impermanence of the mind(GDD-0190, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The mind of the average person is afflicted by greed, aversion, and ignorance and therefore is deluded and impermanent, while the Buddha mind, or the pure mind, is marked by selfless wisdom and compassion and therefore is an unchanging mind. By changing our afflicted mind into a mind of wisdom, we are actually turning impermanence into infinite hope and creating a brighter future.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('ICIzrtgt7IA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'Mindfulness of dharmas as without self(GDD-0191, Master Sheng Yen)', 'To contemplate all phenomena as without a self is to contemplate that our physiological and psychological phenomena and all the material phenomena in our environment are constantly changing. By letting go of our ego or selfish self we will realize the true self, turning the small self into the infinite self, the greater self, which is eternal.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('vSSB9kS5Q24', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'The importance of observing the precepts(GDD-0192, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhist precepts serve as the standard of action for a person and a fundamental moral code for the exemplary Buddhist. They were designed to protect our bodily health, to preserve the harmony of our households, and to ensure the tranquility of society.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('wiWG_2U96Xc', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'The importance of cultivating firm-mindedness(GDD-0193, Master Sheng Yen)', 'In spiritual practice, it is very important to choose one Dharma method and stick to it, believing it to be the best. This gives the practitioner a strong footing and confidence and therefore can be truly beneficial.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('PQBC9R1p8xI', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'How to develop our wisdom(GDD-0194, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Knowledge is not necessarily wisdom. Wisdom means objectivity and freedom from self-centeredness. We gain wisdom by reading the sutras and listening to the Buddhadharma.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('qhyZNMw_Gck', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'The relationship between Buddhism and politics(GDD-0195, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Shakyamuni Buddha travelled among different countries in ancient India to teach the Dharma, hoping to help those countries by influencing their political systems with the ten virtues. Today, Buddhists should know no national borders and not be divided along party lines in applying the Dharma to help humanity and society.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('onzufs_X0S4', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'Buddhists'' stance on participating in politics(GDD-0196, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Nowadays Buddhists should show concern for political affairs while applying Buddhist concepts and the principles of compassion and wisdom. Compassion allows us to be tolerant of people who hold different views. With wisdom we can develop and utilize all the human, social, and political resources in our community, thereby benefitting society.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('N-uSepirjqw', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'Can monastics involve in politics?(GDD-0197, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhist monks can and should serve as elected representatives, to express their own views and share their beliefs with the entire nation so that they will be duly considered, accepted and implemented, thereby benefitting our country and our society.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('zNDqcWdLZiE', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'What are we really so busy for?(GDD-0198, Master Sheng Yen)', 'We have to work hard to insure our own future prospects by achieving merit and virtue, as a way to take responsibility for the past and the future. In addition, we have to work hard to help and benefit all the myriad sentient beings in the universe by using our wisdom and compassion.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('uGMut-wPkqY', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'What attitude we should have when facing the onslaught of disease(GDD-0199, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The \"four sufferings\" of birth, aging, sickness, and death are inevitable. While finding ways to adjust both our body and mind to improve our health, we should be aware and mentally prepared for disease and death. When our hour has come, we should set our mind at rest and go happily and joyfully to the Pure Land of Amitabha.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('7jynTpIXNBY', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrF_FDoLlfpHwgnbQATFx7xN', 'Starting Dharma practice at a young age(GDD-0200, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Any undertaking has to be started in one''s youth so as to lay a solid foundation. We should not wait until we are old to study Buddhism, but should start to practice the moment we hear about the Dharma. Nowadays it''s easier than ever to go about learning and practicing the Buddhadharma, so we want to do that while we can by making the most of our spare time and holidays to get into contact with Buddhism.');
INSERT INTO playlist(pid, cid, title, description) VALUES('PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO','UCBIGwiecylJsQrhTPBKI4Qw', 'GDD(0151-0175)', 'GDD(0151-0175)');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('yk3UWcoV61k', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'Is \"Buddhism of the human world\" against Buddhist tradition? (GDD-151, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Buddhism is meant to solve major human problems of birth, aging, sickness, and death. It is to be practiced in daily life so that we can live without fear and with a sense of security and stability, and that people can live peacefully with each other and care for each other.\n\n\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('lWtTyUeiQ1w', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'Buddhist music (GDD-152, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Music is a basic and universal tool for communicating emotions and, in terms of its positive aspect, can alleviate people''s emotional tension. Similarly, Buddhist chanting or music, being pure, peaceful, joyous and harmonious, helps purify people''s emotions.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('IvP3kt74SRU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'How we can be contented with a simple life to seek inner joy (GDD-153, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Though it is very hard for us to return to simplicity living in modern society, if we can keep a piece of simple and pure nature in our mind by cutting down our wants and having fewer desires, we can still contribute to the protection and conservation of our natural environment.\n.\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('lcR0Q4I_nEw', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'How to live a convenient life in a sustainable manner? (Environmental protection) (GDD-154)', '\"To convenience ourselves but end up inconveniencing others or causing long-term aftereffects is actually to sow bad karmic seeds, harming ourselves and others in the future. Since the garbage problem has become very serious now, if we can create less of garbage and less waste we will be doing a meritorious deed by cutting down on pollution for the benefit of society. \n\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('vxjgczJNH_4', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'How can Ch''an practice be applied in education (GDD-155, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Ch''an practice or meditation as a way to relax and train our body and mind is worth promoting in that it enables us to become gentler and milder in temperament, stronger and more stable in their personality. \n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('JFJyW4_0LfI', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'Living in the present (GDD-156, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"With more and more information and knowledge to occupy our minds nowadays, it''s all the more important to make best use of our time. Living in the present, appreciateing the present, and enjoying the present is actually the most economical way to use the time.\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('v4EncYcf_UQ', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'How should women plan their life? (GDD-157, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"The times, society, and family structures may have changed, men and women cannot exchange their natural roles. In terms of work in society and intellectual ability, women and men should be equal, but in terms of taking care of children and home, women have more patience, resilience, endurance and they are more stable and better equipped.\n\n\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Xhh6mXtfn90', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'How can women face up to karma and eliminate obstacles? (GDD-158, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Karmic obstruction means our evil karma that has accumulated in past lives and our occupation that keeps us from taking up the teachings of the Buddhadharma. We should be broad-mined or use psychological concepts to make adjustments and not lose hope.\n\n\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('KUGF3a6cfYk', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'How to become a graceful, modern beauty (GDD-159, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Exterior beauty without internal substance is only superficial and false beauty. True face with honesty, sincerity, and compassion in mind is the beauty within, and therefore the genuine beauty. Beauty and ugliness are determined in the mind, not by one''s outward appearance.\n\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('CIYiufCjUeA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'How to pursue a bright, beautiful, and fulfilling marriage (GDD-160, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Husband and wife are two distinct people from different backgrounds and so may have different ways of thinking about children, home, finances, careers, and how to deal with things. Husband and wife should respect each other, learn from each other, forgive and be understanding towards each other, and care for each other.\n \"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('fLUZ_6Iw4pA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'How can one emerge from the game of pursuit of wealth(GDD-161, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Pursuing wealth for individual self-interest will bring harm to oneself and others. Instead, by seeking wealth for all society or all human beings without harming others, we are cultivating blessings and accumulating merit. \n\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('UoII57z3UoY', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'A look at \"life plan\" from the Buddhist perspective(GDD-162, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Life planning should cover endless lives and go beyond the material aspect. We can plan our life by setting a direction for the growth of our spiritual cultivation and realizing where our talents lie, our qualities and abilities, and what our resources are.\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('A7c42OXqabQ', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'The correct way to view and care for our body to make use of it for spiritual practice(GDD-163)', '\"Though Buddhism teaches us not to be attached to our physical body, it is a tool for the practice of the Way, a medium through which we cultivate wisdom. We should use it properly, and care for it by protecting our physical health through doing exercises, sitting meditation, or simply relaxing our body and mind at any time or place.\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('mr7PG8ICXZU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'How can we elude the temptations and fetters of material indulgence(GDD-164, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"The higher the level of spiritual involvement in one''s life, the lower one''s degree of dependence on material goods. However, to do without material things completely is not something Buddhism advocates. Our use of material should be appropriate to who we are, suitable for the situation we are in, and suitable for the time.\n \n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('HkZzrW4cHxc', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'How to attain freedom and ease in emotions(GDD-0165, Master Sheng Yen)', 'There are three levels of emotion: passing moods, feelings, and noble sentiments. Buddhism encourages the elimination of passing moods, and the harmonization, purification, and exaltation of rationality and emotion, thereby developing compassion and wisdom.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('gxpaAtbWS5o', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'Interpersonal skills(GDD-0166, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The suffering of meeting the hated and the suffering of parting with the beloved reflect the affliction we have in our interpersonal relationships. Buddhism helps us deal with these problems by teaching us to let go of our self-centeredness through repentance and transference of merit.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('AferNks9OPo', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'The art of work(GDD-0167, Master Sheng Yen)', 'As a responsibility to contribute to society in which we help each other to live and exist, we should employ \"ordinary mind\" to do what we should, what we can, and what we are given to do, while seeking to improve ourselves by constantly learning from more capable or talented people.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('SM61kNK5b24', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'How to transcend the things that happen to us in life (GDD-0168, Master Sheng Yen)', 'When our mind changes with the environment, then it is subject to afflictions. We should be the master of our own mind by not being affected by the situations or circumstances we are in, while seeking to improve the environment from an impartial perspective and with a broad mind.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('vSo0SA0ot_8', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'How to build self-confidence(GDD-0169, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Fame, status, wealth, power and influence do not help us to build confidence. To build true confidence, one must not be affected by wealth or poverty, high or low status, and life or death, and have a right understanding of ourselves.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('2MNGKbI2GIw', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'Why can''t success, wealth, power, and status bring us happiness?(GDD-0170, Master Sheng Yen)', 'According to Confucius, those who can establish merit, virtue, or words are successful people. In terms of Buddhism, those who can achieve peace of mind are also successful people, and attaining Buddhahood is the greatest success.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('67J5mD5nSKQ', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'How to find our true self(GDD-0171, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Most people have misconception of the self and therefore become the slaves of the external environment. To find our true self is to learn to be our own master and govern our mind, while trying our best to do what we can, learn what we should learn, and continually correct ourselves.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('-KRuLqlQLcs', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'How to own up to our mistakes (GDD-0172, Master Sheng Yen)', 'To encourage people to own up to their own mistakes, we must accept responsibility for our mistakes and also accept other people''s admission of their mistakes. By bravely owning up when we make a mistake, we will be more able to avoid repeating the same mistake, which is the true meaning of repentance.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('wiRp1QcJH48', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'How to transcend the basic human desires for food and sex(GDD-0173, Master Sheng Yen)', 'To truly transcend our self, we must constantly make progress by letting go of our views, affirm, encourage, and recognize others by letting go of our self-centeredness, as well as give of ourselves without thinking of getting anything back.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('FuVjj_BzvRo', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'How to cope when one loses his social status(GDD-0174, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Social status actually means the roles one plays in society and should be regarded from the angle of equality, and not from the point of view of its differences. As long as one plays one'' roles appropriately and fulfills their respective duties, then one already has a social status and will be approved by society.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('ltrgEhp0tT0', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGT_FFhy6GOYMH9e5G4-QIO', 'The pursuit of freedom and dignity (GDD-0175, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Instead of trying to obtain freedom and dignity from outside ourselves, we should earn them by first giving others their freedom and acting like we deserve our dignity, instead of trying to extend our own individuality and fighting for dignity.');
INSERT INTO playlist(pid, cid, title, description) VALUES('PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p','UCBIGwiecylJsQrhTPBKI4Qw', 'GDD(0126-0150)', '');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('9Ta0HRPaTT4', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'How to choose  a suitable \"Dharma-gate,\" or method of practice, for oneself(GDD-126)', '\"The most suitable Dharma-gate is the one we come into contact with and are using right now, which we should believe to be the best. One can make small adjustments on the spiritual path, but one shouldn''t frequently change one''s spiritual path, for the most effective and reliable practice should be a deep commitment to one single Dharma-gate. \n\n  \"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('2Er3EeMqeAc', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'The ritual of taking refuge in the Three Jewels(GDD-127, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Though reading sutras or practicing the Dharma by oneself can be beneficial, it is not as good as  having taken refuge in the three jewels in that it marks one''s aspiration to learn the Buddhadharma in its true sense from a source of transmission, and a collective spirit to enhance one''s spiritual practice.\n\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('tHJTYNYuSZU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'Individual vs. group cultivation(GDD-128, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The Buddhist term \"seven classes of disciples\" indicates that Buddhism has always encouraged group cultivation, in which practitioners can encourage and correct each other and thus help each other grow better, faster, as well benefit from wise teachers and fellow practitioners spiritually.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Izx6gSfW3g4', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'The difference between creating and dispelling karmic ties(GDD-129, Master Sheng Yen)', 'To form good karmic ties with all sentient beings is to aid them through the Buddhadharma, in which we use the Dharma to help others help themselves or use material objects to release other people''s suffering unconditionally.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Q0ST0AhJ4WU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'The difference between a Buddha''s and a Bodhisattva''s deliverance(GDD-130, Master Sheng Yen)', 'A bodhisattva is an enlightened sentient being, who benefits himself and others in leaving behind afflictions, gaining wisdom, and ultimately attaining Buddhahood. While a buddha is perfect in both blessings and wisdom, one who has realized no-self and delivers sentient beings without thinking there are any to deliver.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('otz_kHS20hI', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'Freeing captive animals—its meaning and methods(GDD-131, Master Sheng Yen)', 'It is best for animals to live in natural environments, so animal protection or preservation is a better way for the purpose of protecting lives, instead of releasing captive animals into an environment in which they cannot survive.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('abcquC26m8o', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'How to face predicaments and overcome obstacles in our lives(GDD-132, Master Sheng Yen)', 'From the Buddhist perspective, life is suffering and the process from birth till death is all surrounded by difficulties. We should face this reality of life with mental preparation and a positive way of thinking, taking it as a necessary training to aid our development.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('IZLvUXuWnYU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'How to lead a rational emotional life(GDD-133, Master Sheng Yen)', 'A rational emotional life is one with emotions and rationality in harmony. If we are stuck with an emotional problem, we should use the Buddhadharma to channel our mind and have a new way of thinking so as to overcome the problem.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('1qmA1LuuhGY', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'The meaning of work(GDD-134, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Having a job means having the means to sustain our daily living and a way to contribute to society in which people work to produce the living environment and conditions we enjoy. We should take going to work as performing a service to society and forming good karmic affinities with others, which will in turn increase our own blessings.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('P7NKLxftjqc', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'How to achieve eternal spiritual liberation(GDD-135, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism teaches about impermanence, meaning that there is nothing truly eternal and unchanging. The ultimate meaning of eternal is to face reality and live our lives in a down-to-earth way, remain clear and free of any vexation or affliction, and develop faith to sustain our spirituality.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('TmHERVY1m_0', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'The meaning of demonic tests(GDD-136, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Except for the demon of death, the other three types of demon reflect our own mental afflictions or unrighteous thoughts. So the best way to avoid demonic obstacles is to try our best to cultivate the path, maintain right views, and use correct methods of practice.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('zTl5PyhLSgA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'Should one have faith in the sutras?(GDD-137, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhist sutras are records of the Buddha''s teachings in different places and with different people, and therefore have different effects. Although the sutras are not necessarily all the words of the Buddha, they all represent the basic Buddhist principles and so are useful and beneficial.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('VOWCs7OLfGE', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'Are the Buddhist sutras really difficult to read and understand?(GDD-138, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhist special terms are what make Buddhist sutras seem difficult to understand. Any person can understand the sutras if they really want to understand them. As long as we are willing to spend time to learn and understand, we will get to know what they mean.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('OAp45f0ZHXA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'Is Buddhism a pessimistic, world-weary religion?(GDD-139, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The reason why Buddhism teaches that everything in this world is suffering is to encourage people to transcend the world and attain liberation by devoting themselves to the world, practicing the Dharma, following the path to enlightenment, and cultivating bodhisattva practices.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('9unxNzMG-0Y', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'The true meaning of kalpa(GDD-140, Master Sheng Yen)', 'A kalpa is a vast unit of time to measure the coming and going of a world system. Though our world will come to its kalpa of destruction and eventually the kalpa of emptiness, we need not worry but should practice diligently in order to be reborn in the Western World of Ultimate Bliss.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Ze6qEZM-kaU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'Is praying really useful?(GDD-141, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism shares many functions of other great religions, but it is also a philosophy and a form of practical ethics we should practice ourselves in order to achieve liberation and attain Buddhahood, the ultimate goal of practicing Buddhism. Prayer serves as an aid to this purpose and whether it is useful or not all depends on our sincerity and faith.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('F8Ug9muropQ', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'Should we take the advice of  Buddhist masters with a grain of salt?(GDD-142, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism centers on the Three Jewels: Buddha, Dharma, Sangha. Buddhism has three criteria: rely on the Dharma, not those who teach it; rely on the spirit, not the letter; rely on the ultimate meaning, not any provisional truth; rely on wisdom, not merely intellectual understanding. These four are called the \"four reliances.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('e7LrgNeaQ7o', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'What role does Buddhism play in the effort of purifying people''s minds?(GDD-143, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Purifying people''s minds is the basis for purifying the environment and society. Buddhism helps purify human minds by offering concepts and methods of practice to improve people''s family lives, enhance individual character, and influence society in a positive way.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('L069esCjCR0', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'The true meaning of emptiness(GDD-144, Master Sheng Yen)', 'In Buddhism, \"\"emptiness\"\" means that all phenomena, either material or psychological, are not eternal and unchanging. Therefore we should remain undisturbed by them in our minds and don''t fall victim to all kinds of negative, contaminated mental reactions.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('I2VjN5p3-fw', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'What distinguishes Buddhism from other religions?(GDD-145, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism speaks of causes and conditions instead of a Creator God, or the idea that God created the universe. It acknowledges the existence of deities, ghosts, and all kinds of spirits, considers them as various types of sentient beings, and sees them equally.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('OL1-msmjrec', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'Is the law of karmic cause and effect applicable in the present time?(GDD-146, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Karmic force means the effect of our bodily, mental, and verbal actions performed in the past. The law of karmic cause and effect spanning the three periods, namely the past, the present, and the future, actually points us toward hope, tells us not to despair, and helps us experience peace of mind.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('vaD6l53Jw60', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'Using correct religious concepts to help purify society(GDD-147, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhist principles of moral thought and action can be incorporated in school education in terms of civic or social education, in order to help improve social climate and the way of the world by purifying people''s minds.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('aW_ARzs9E40', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'Can the Buddhadharma and medical theory complement each other?(GDD-148, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The Buddhadharma helps us face and accept illness with peace of mind and hope through the transformation of our psychological feeling. Without suffering in our mind, our physical illnesses will ease and even be cured.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('d6YkYIjLLnI', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'How does the Buddhadharma explain impermanence?(GDD-149, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Impermanence is the reality of phenomena in the process of time, where good and bad alternate. It teaches us to be aware and alert with a sense of crisis and preparedness, while living our lives with content.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('_gFqKa0ctBU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrE1AEPcwgUe2uIfu3D0_W7p', 'Buddhist householder and a non-Buddhist householder(GDD-0150, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Lay practitioners can certainly practice Buddhism in a family setting by learning the bodhisattva''s way, developing wisdom by not being vexed by problems in life and cultivating compassion by showing care and love to their family members.');
INSERT INTO playlist(pid, cid, title, description) VALUES('PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf','UCBIGwiecylJsQrhTPBKI4Qw', 'GDD(0101-0125)', '');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Op97WV2ncNg', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'How do we choose our Chan practice teachers?(GDD-101, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Most people do need a Chan Practice teacher. They should find a teacher with correct understanding of Buddhism, sound practice, with a clear mind and good skills in guiding others.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('ehS3aU-LpOw', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'The meaning of Drop the butcher''s knife and immediately become a Buddha (GDD-102, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Everyone has an innate buddha-nature and has the potential to become a buddha. As long as we stop doing evil and start to practice the six paramitas (six perfections), we are heading toward the Buddhahood.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('JaFYTUwu8mg', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'The purpose of sutra recitation and mantra chanting(GDD-103, Master Sheng Yen)', 'There are two functions of reciting the sutras and mantras. It helps us to self-reflect whether our acts are in accord with the sutras. It is also a meditation practice.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('wAdWNdAsV_g', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'Must Ch''an practice always involve sitting meditation?(GDD-104, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Ch''an practice is to train our mind to be calm, quiet, and pure so that we can be liberated from afflictive emotions. Practicing concentration starts from contemplation and a right mindfulness, and it doesn''t have to involve sitting down in meditation.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('nJuzle3u8UM', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'Is pilgrimage is a form of practice?(GDD-105, Master Sheng Yen)', 'As a way of practice, pilgrimage is a sacred journey of worship to pay respect rather than sightsee. It helps develop our faith and encourage us to live out the spirit of the Buddha or Bodhisattva.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('18J01N0Qzq4', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'The merits of giving (GDD-106, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Giving with expectations of future rewards is a merit with outflows and can only lead to blessings for human and heavenly beings. While giving without seeking anything in return is a Buddhist virtue that will help one transcend samsara and attain great liberation.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('FFqHK0g6aXU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'Contention (GDD-107, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Fighting comes from greed and desire. Selfish desires are insatiable and will only bring affliction. Instead we should turn them into purified desires, as a vow to benefit both ourselves and others.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('XoTQKQtivxI', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'Competition (GDD-108, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Competitiveness has its own positive function in that it brings out our right efforts and urges us to work harder and strive for better. But at the meantime we should also avoid either arrogance or the sense of inferiority and simply give our best effort.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('VVDoaggONEQ', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'How to deal with envy and jealousy (GDD-109, Master Sheng Yen)', 'A fundamental affliction in terms of Buddhism, jealousy has to do with anger or hatred in that people tend to feel that if they don''t get what they want, then nobody else should get it either. The remedy to jealousy is to practice rejoicing in others'' meritorious deeds, and the best way to avoid being envied is to be modest.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('QBL3_h86_-M', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'Anger and hatred (GDD-110, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Anger and hatred make us lose our wisdom and calmness. Instead we should try to improve our own situation and change our mindset with spiritual practice, and to be kind and compassionate toward ourselves and all sentient beings.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('6lnXc3IbQD0', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'Can visiting Buddhist monasteries and eminent monks be considered spiritual practice?(GDD-111)', 'Visiting Buddhist monasteries and eminent monks to learn different methods of practice is good, reliable, and useful only under the condition that it is done through a wise teacher''s advice and guidance.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('p4UzzkWsldk', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'How to enhance the quality of life(GDD-112, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Talking about the quality of living without taking actions to enrich our spiritual life will be empty. To improve the quality of living, we must have a cultural, spiritual, and religious life. But only religious belief, practice, and experience with faith can provide a truly fulfilling life.\n \n\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('bzs_GqFzHh4', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'Success and failure(GDD-113, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"There is no such thing as true success in this world; there is only the process. Success and failure are just an illusion; it all depends on the causes and conditions. Instead of pursuing success we should simply have a direction for which we can put forth our efforts without expecting and being attached to the result.\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('UFW79Fq4IWM', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'How does Buddhadharma account for disability?(GDD-114, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Events of this life are karmic results from our actions of past lives. For the disabled who have accepted the Buddhist concept, we can tell them to practice and repent so that their karmic hindrances will diminish. Otherwise we should encourage them to regard themselves as bodhisattvas manifesting in this world as a model to influence others in a positive way. \n\n\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('H3SeG3Qn7C8', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'How do we overcome an external limitation, and restore our internal faith?(GDD-115)', '\"Some people may be handicapped, but their mental capacities are exactly the same as everyone else''s. Through psychological guidance and religious faith, one can transform one''s perceptions and be a healthy person by maintaining a healthy mind and outlook.\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('lnIwIhgmkW8', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'Resolving attachment, hatred, passion and resentment(GDD-116, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Mental and emotional afflictions come from our attachment to our feelings and thinking. We should resolve such afflictions by understanding karmic causality as well as the working of causes and conditions. \n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('UI6Sohs-y4Q', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'How to transcend birth, aging, illness and death(GDD-117, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism teaches that birth, aging, sickness, and death are all suffering in that they are changing, false image. Even when there is joy it is transient and not forever. To transcend samsara we should prepare our savings of merit to be born in Amitabha Buddha''s Pure Land of Ultimate Bliss, our final settling place.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('8NMgftCJPyE', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'How to achieve the state of one-pointed concentration(GDD-118, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"All Buddhist sects in China advocate recitation of Buddha''s name for it is the simplest method for spiritual practice, which is proven to be effective to the greatest number of people and has been most commonly used. Buddha-name recitation brings numerous benefits: spiritual response, protection from Dharma-protecting deities, elimination of evil thoughts, peace of mind and body, benefits in the present life, rebirth to Amitabha''s Pure Land.\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('RTW5ms7k010', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'Practicing Buddhism(GDD-119, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Whether we will make progress in our practice of Buddhism  depends on our willpower and willingness. To keep practicing diligently we can constantly relive our initial aspiration for bodhi or enlightenment and keep pushing forward. Every step forward in the process equals an accomplishment, and we are reaping the benefits while we are practicing.\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('1-Fj51MqO9I', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'How to enhance and purify love(GDD-120, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism advocates the ultimate form of love, which is causeless compassion, or unconditional compassion. To practice unconditional compassion is to practice giving or show concern to others on an equal basis without expecting any payback or reward.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('cNfxQxO4sz4', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'The merits of reciting sutras(GDD-121, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Reciting sutras benefits oneself and one''s family and represents spreading the teachings of the Buddhadharma. It can also benefit other sentient beings who are hearing the recitation. Its ultimate purpose is that we observe the teachings of the sutra and act accordingly.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('S4nz88wUiD0', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'The meaning of sutras(GDD-122, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"In general, the essential teachings of the sutras are about the analysis of the mind and the resolution of affliction. The whole Buddhist canon contains a massive collection of sutras, but their basic principles are \"\"suffering, emptiness, impermanence and selflessness,\"\" and their main idea is to help us attain liberation from the sea of samsara.\n\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('QO7E48Pg2rQ', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'The effects of chanting mantras(GDD-123, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The power of mantra comes from the merit attained by a certain ghost, deity, Bodhisattva, or Buddha, as well as from the mental power or power of concentration of the person reciting it. The efficacy of mantras lies in faith.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('8BBOlDCOgww', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'The difference between Buddha and God(GDD-124, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"In Buddhism, \"\"sin\"\" is the bad karma one brings from one''s past lives since beginningless time; it reflects the idea of causality, or cause and effect. To eliminate our karma and change our fate, we are supposed to follow the Buddha''s teachings and practice accordingly, and that is the way to achieve salvation or redemption.\n \"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('2bIxWqDyfVM', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHbE-8tyov95ZDk51BorSZf', 'Is enlightenment equivalent to Buddhahood?(GDD-125, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Orthodox Buddhism teaches about enlightenment but also teaches us not to become obsessed with pursuing enlightenment. Enlightenment in its true sense means hearing the Dharma, experiencing the Buddhadharma for ourselves, and then acting accordingly to change ourselves, instead of some mystic experiences, though they can reinforce our faith for the path.\n\n\"');
INSERT INTO playlist(pid, cid, title, description) VALUES('PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE','UCBIGwiecylJsQrhTPBKI4Qw', 'GDD(0076-0100)', '');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('2Lz6Orqh25E', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'Are the five Confucian human relationships at odds with the concept of equality?(GDD-76 )', 'Ethical codes are a system of order to define the role or position from which individuals should fulfill their respective responsibilities. They are there to protect us by conferring on us a number of rights, allowing our society to operate in an orderly fashion, which reflects the spirit of equality.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('M4xgvOgzYm4', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'Cooperation and submission(GDD-77 Master Sheng Yen)', 'The true meaning of cooperation is that through combined efforts people will be able to achieve their commonly needed and pursued work. Cooperation implies the need for division of labor and requires communication, coordination, and mutual understanding.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('YzCtmYqcwwA', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'Which is more important, the individual or the group?(GDD-78 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism advocates communality and helping one another based on harmony and equality by considering everyone''s needs. Through group practice in this spirit individuals are able to develop faster and follow the more correct path.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('L9qwIpFpbn8', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'How should we view special privileges? (GDD-79 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Responsibilities and powers can''t be separated, in that our rights are in fact our duties. In terms of Buddhism, life itself is a power we should put to good use in seeking wisdom and cultivating blessings so as to benefit ourselves and others.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('e0muOZOlQvc', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'How do we maintain good judgment?(GDD-80 Master Sheng Yen)', 'To have sober judgment, we should keep ourselves from getting swept up and confused in new things or ideas by observing things dispassionately and making rational choice, or otherwise by following people with wisdom or intelligence.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('jpSb0z6y-no', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'How do the Buddhas view sentient beings?(GDD-81 Master Sheng Yen)', 'The Buddha sees all sentient beings as equal and as future buddhas, although they still have afflictions. The Buddha is an educator who helps us eliminate our afflictions with his impartial compassion and selfless wisdom, without thinking about how many beings he has delivered.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('nf0nwTp3-84', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'Belief, understanding, practice and verification(GDD-82 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism places equal emphasis on both understanding and practice, and encourages people to immediately put to practice what they know. Practice and understanding should correspond to each other, although we can still practice Buddhism and therefore benefit from it even if we don''t understand.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('gewEaBAmVBE', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'Appearances and reality(GDD-83 Master Sheng Yen)', '\"In our current society, it is necessary to use publicity to call on people to participate in doing good deeds and hope others to follow suit. Ch''an Buddhism is down-to-earth and sensible; it encourages people to put in effort to practice so as to benefit physically and spiritually instead of putting emphasis on mystical experiences.\n  \n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('mXJXrKEzo0c', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'The true meaning of Ch''an(GDD-84 Master Sheng Yen)', '\"The true meaning of Ch''an is wisdom and compassion, and the meaning of meditative absorption is not to be affected by our environment and not to be subject to any temptation. Ch''an Buddhism teaches that concentration and wisdom are one, with which we are able to deal with people and events objectively without giving rise to mental affliction.\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('b6lwA_eTGqs', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'Simple and easy ways of practicing Ch''an for people who lead busy lives(GDD-85 Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Ch''an practice is in everyday activities; our daily lives can be a time and place of spiritual practice. It all comes down to whether the mind is stable, whether our minds and bodies are unified, and whether we can be unperturbed inside.\n\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('3QMadvSp1ec', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'Do Ch''an masters also have to observe the precepts?(GDD-86 Master Sheng Yen)', 'A Ch''an master should also observe the precepts, otherwise he cannot have the power to move and transform others. A fully enlightened person must be one who can observe the precepts purely before transcending them all and without being bound by them.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Uz9gtfw-a00', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'Mundane Ch''an vs. modern Ch''an(GDD-87 Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Ch''an Buddhism originated with Shakyamuni Buddha and its essential spirit has never varied. It places great emphasis on daily life and the experience of direct awakening. By practicing Ch''an, even when one cannot achieve enlightenment, one is certainly planting the roots of good karma and will be able to have fewer afflictions and develop more wisdom.\n\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('m9vxoMMUmEU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'Twin practice of both Ch''an and Pure Land methods(GDD-88 Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Pure Land Buddhism advocates reciting the Buddha''s name or mindfulness of the Buddha, based on the teaching that the mind itself is buddha. Ch''an Buddhism teaches that as the mind is purified, so is the land purified. Reciting Buddha''s name and the approach of Ch''an Buddhism are essentially identical. Nonetheless, Ch''an practice methods are the foundation for a stabilized mind and can better ensure one''s possibility of birth in the Western Pure Land.\n\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('tmFjMOAtkuE', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'Enlightenment vs. seeing the true nature of one''s mind(GDD-89 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Enlightenment means the development of wisdom, the perfection of character, and the eradication of the afflictions, and it all lies in whether we are willing to let go ouf our ego or self. To achieve this we must frist realize conceptually that all things are without substance, and then use Buddhist methods to transform our minds.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('JQSJ5WFtKLM', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'The difference between gradual enlightenment and sudden enlightenment(GDD-90 Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Gradual enlightenment and sudden enlightenment serve the same purpose. As long as one becomes enlightened, it is good. It depends on one''s karmic capacity whether one will attain gradual or sudden enlightenment. After attaining enlightenment one still has to practice so as to achieve the state of perfect buddhahood. \n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('5-QRJ_JI52M', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'Deriving wisdom from concentration(GDD-91 Master Sheng Yen)', '\"In terms of meditation, concentration means a progress of practice from a scattered, chaotic mind to a focused mind, and then to a unified mind, at which point one will have more objectivity. In terms of Ch''an, selfless wisdom is achieved when one lets go of one''s self-centeredness and hence becomes undisturbed by the environment.\n \n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('RsQKCO8kcVc', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'Spiritual capacity(GDD-92 Master Sheng Yen)', 'The root of goodness and that of affliction, or ignorance, exist side by side. As ignorance diminishes the good roots grow. By developing our wisdom and compassion, we are actually increasing our spiritual capacity and developing our good roots, which is the Buddha-nature, and therefore transform ourselves from an ordinary person.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('H-87suTRJog', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'Seven-day Ch''an retreat - why fixed on  a 7-day span, and not more or less?(GDD-93 Master Sheng Yen)', 'The practice of seven-day Ch''an retreat comes from the idea of setting a time period to live a pure life and practice meditation. The timeframe of seven days is related to the movement of the universe and marks a cycle. Nowadays, seven-day Ch''an retreats are open to lay practitioners to participate in the practice.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('GtvPYkPM0Fs', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'The relationship between Ch''an Buddhism and Chinese culture(GDD-94 Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Chinese culture and Chinese Buddhism influenced each other and are inseparable. Ancient China, influenced by Confucianism and Taoism, was a rather humanistic and naturalistic society, so Buddhism in China has become an earthly religion, a unique quality of Ch''an Buddhism. \n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('NYSM1dBOCQY', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'How Westerners differ from Asians in practicing Ch''an and applying Ch''an to their lives(GDD-95 )', 'Ch''an got to the West after World War II mainly attributed to two systems of Japanese Zen, advocated by Kyozan Joshu Sasaki and Daisetsu Teitaro Suzuki respectively. Although Westerners approach Ch''an somewhat differently than Asians do, they both appreciate its physical and mental benefits for their lives.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('iUaDyhfPnPY', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'Buddhist tradition of transmission(GDD-96 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Transmission, which is a \"meeting of minds\" in terms of the insight into reality, marks the source of one''s Dharma-body or Dharma lineage, and serves to prove or verify one''s state of enlightenment.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('RmjabY8aMOI', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'Demonic state vs. enlightened state(GDD-97 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Demonic states may come from our bodily reactions or psychological afflictions when we are engaged in meditation practice. Most people enter demonic states because when they practice their mind is not very pure. So the best way to do meditation is to have no attachment or craving, letting go of trying to get anywhere at all.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('ROWfv26X6fc', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'Solitary retreat - its qualification requirements and benefits(GDD-98 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Solitary retreat is an opportunity for individual practice, to focus solely on studying the Buddhist canon, doing prostration to the Buddha, reciting Buddha''s name, or sitting in meditation, among other methods of practice. One can benefit a lot from it if one has a good command of the concepts and methods of practice.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('wccUFcgMJ9g', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'Advantageous effects of meditation(GDD-99 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Meditation can help us balance our body and our mind, bring out our potential wisdom, and develop our potential physical and mental power. While Chan practice enables us to eliminate our attachment to our self-centeredness, and therefore attain liberation and freedom.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('_cYeklUPkOk', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrHlK_17jrGJIFw5VX81nwIE', 'Mutual affinity in Ch''an Buddhism - Meeting of the minds(GDD-100, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Intuitive meeting of minds is pointing directly to the human mind regarding the insight to reality. This requires one to have experienced some degree of enlightenment, which is beyond the expression of words.');
INSERT INTO playlist(pid, cid, title, description) VALUES('PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e','UCBIGwiecylJsQrhTPBKI4Qw', 'GDD(0051-0075)', '');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('ZSJbJQa1cfk', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'What does it mean to wear Buddha beads?(GDD-51 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Wearing Buddha beads reminds one to pay attention to one''s daily actions. Reciting the Buddha''s name signifies eliminating one''s vexation. One can recite as many times as one wishes but the important thing is to focus while one is reciting.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('v8LdodI3Iew', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'School education(GDD-52 Master Sheng Yen)', 'The fundamental reason for education issues lies in the human mind. The pursuit of personal freedom should not compromise ethical relations between teachers and students. Integrity and self-awareness are the key remedy to educational problems.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('O4qCP00IxAY', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'Drug abuse(GDD-53 Master Sheng Yen)', 'People who use drugs lack a sense of security and belonging. Buddhism can help them establish a new view of life and sense of confidence by changing their outlooks and giving them encouragement.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Ldo78MEzXDI', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'Should we let prophecies affect our lives?(GDD-54 Master Sheng Yen)', 'From a Buddhist perspective, everything arises from the interaction of causes and conditions. Instead of believing in prophecies, we should believe in cause and effect, and that we can change our fate by changing our way of thinking.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('tBehYcsWXaM', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'How to establish one''s own senses of security and stability(GDD-55 Master Sheng Yen)', 'The Buddha taught that life is impermanent and the world is fragile and fraught with danger. By being mentally prepared, having a positive thinking, and cultivating merit with faith, we''ll have a better guarantee of security.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('AMYEgSv59eQ', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'The relationship between our thoughts and behaviors(GDD-56 Master Sheng Yen)', 'We should carefully examine our bodily, verbal, and mental actions, which will result in a karmic force that affects our fate. The mind is our master, and can change our fate and the world for better or for worse.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('bCFk65sTS04', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'The relationship between human and the Buddha(GDD-57 Master Sheng Yen)', 'All sentient beings have the Buddha-nature and can attain Buddhahood. But Buddhist teachings are targeted at human beings, who are required to fulfill their ethical responsibilities and be compassionate toward others.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('UvGMB3UaUZ0', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'The difference between human and the Buddha(GDD-58 Master Sheng Yen)', 'A Buddha is one who has achieved no-self and delivers sentient beings with wisdom and compassion, without thought of deliverance itself. An ordinary person circles around a selfish self and cares about gain and loss. We should transform ourselves by learning the bodhisattva way.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('jE6WhMZI0Ns', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'Bodhisattva of infant-like practice and the Bodhisattva precepts(GDD-59 Master Sheng Yen)', 'A bodhisattva of infant-like practice is one who has just generated the bodhi-mind to become a Buddha. Those who practice Mahayana Buddhism should learn the bodhisattva spirit and are encouraged to receive the Bodhisattva Precepts.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('thfGQ2ay5tM', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'How do we achieve no-self from ego?(GDD-60 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Although Buddhism teaches about no-self, the Buddha''s teachings begin with the self and require us to affirm and develop ourselves by being our own master, and thus grow in merit and virtue and develop toward the road to Buddhahood.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('uHXo1JbNZ0s', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'Self-affirmation (Part I)(GDD-61 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Self-affirmation is to take up responsibility for our actions in the past, present, and future. It lies in whether we can control ourselves or be our own master, by first knowing our own faults and strengths.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('-zVS6jbPXIY', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'Self-affirmation (Part II - methods)(GDD-62 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhist practice methods enable us to discover our own faults and take responsibility for our own actions, which is the true meaning of repentance. We should also repent for not having done what we should be doing in terms of Buddhist practice.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('e2zaLcgBEfo', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'Why should we repent? How should we repent?(GDD-63 Master Sheng Yen)', 'To repent, either to our own conscience, to the person we have done a disservice, or in public, is to express responsibilities for ourselves. By repenting on a daily basis we can gradually purify our body and mind, and therefore eliminate our karmic obstacles.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('awWAVex4L9o', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'Buddhist repentance rituals(GDD-64 Master Sheng Yen)', 'The contents of different repentance rituals are compiled based on different Buddhist sutras. Repentance rituals can serve as a way of practice, help one cure one''s karmic illness and achieve peace of mind when facing karmic obstacles or receiving karmic retribution.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('JKydAf9cvYw', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'Buddhist etiquettes(GDD-65 Master Sheng Yen)', 'True etiquette lies in internal sincerity, respect, and thankfulness. We should show etiquette in our mental, verbal, and bodily actions. By regarding all sentient beings as bodhisattvas and treating them equally, we will have politeness in mind on all occasions.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('LSeZYicHsWk', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'Why do we promote joint weddings, joint birthday (GDD-66 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Dharma Drum Mountain promotes joint weddings, joint birthday celebrations, and joint funerals as a way to remind people of the true meaning of these occasions by introducing Buddhist concepts and methods, and thereby encouraging respect, frugality, the sense of responsibility, and harmony in society.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('LovGgvcOOIE', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'Democratic spirit in Buddhism(GDD-67 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Democratic spirit in Buddhism is reflected in the six points of reverent harmony or unity in a monastery, where monastics are required to achieve the same views through communication and consensus voting.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('kvn21DpLMwU', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'What is the relationship between the Buddhist precepts and the law?(GDD-68 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Democracy and law complements each other. The rule of laws, which are legislated in accordance with the views of the people, ensures a society''s peace and security. Buddhist precepts were set down based on the social customs and conventions and in accordance with the people''s needs in the Buddha''s time, to safeguard practitioners'' dharmic consciousness.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('IymOdYp-i-E', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'How to draw the line between what''s reasonable and what''s unreasonable?(GDD-69 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Whether things are reasonable or unreasonable depends on the reasoning of the majority, logical thinking, common sense, and judgment based on experience. In a group setting, we must find a consensus everybody is comfortable and happy with.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('QWdeYVtcHWQ', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'Personal views vs. conventional principles(GDD-70 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Personal views reflect people''s judgments in their own place and time, which have their reasons and should be understood. But if one is very insistent on one''s own opinions, it might compromise the harmony of all society. The best way is to continue offering our opinions to help while having the magnanimity to see them rejected.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('rmCX2yrEE5E', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'Subjectivity and objectivity(GDD-71 Master Sheng Yen)', 'There is no conflict between subjectivity and objectivity because they are relative. Objectivity is achieved by bringing together everyone''s subjective opinions, weighing up their importance, and making a best choice while respecting everyone''s subjective consciousness.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Cj1lYcWXumY', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'Being active vs. being passive(GDD-72 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Active is when a person takes the initiative, with mental preparedness. Passive is when we have to face and deal with a situation. But active and passive basically coordinate with each other and reflect the Buddhist idea of causes and conditions.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('VwAsAyayNNs', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'Adaptation and change(GDD-73 Master Sheng Yen)', 'When joining a new society, environment, or group, we must try to adapt to it first. Once we have adapted and realize that there are areas in need of change, we can seek gradual improvements by offering our personal opinions while listening to all objections and differences of opinion.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('f4UJhNA60fg', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'Spiritual practice(GDD-74 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Spiritual practice is about mending our own bodily, verbal, and mental action. In addition to reciting sutras, prostrating to the Buddha, sitting in meditation, among other methods of practice, we can also practice while at work by putting our heart into our work.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('sF4g3_aQXmg', 'PLz2LIY6rQQrGmEd8HuriUUwtp-sgRJd-e', 'Mundane dharmas and supramundane dharmas(GDD-75 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Mundane dharmas are that which is dualistic and relative and involves a self and others, while supramundane dharmas are that which transcends time and space. To transcend the mundane means to be liberated from the relative and dualistic mind, instead of leaving the mundane existence.');
INSERT INTO playlist(pid, cid, title, description) VALUES('PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05','UCBIGwiecylJsQrhTPBKI4Qw', 'GDD(0026-0050)', 'GDD(0026-0050)');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('6Wwr5TQ2-Vw', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Organ donation(GDD-26, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Organs are parts of the body made up of the four elements and are therefore a false appearance one shouldn''t attach to. Donating one''s organs is an act of letting go of one''s ego. It is a form of giving and has great merit.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('WPLFz8aPcgU', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Birth (Part I)(GDD-27, Master Sheng Yen)', 'People without children can share their time by doing volunteer works or taking care of other people''s children. People should raise their adopted children as their own child. Parents with handicapped child should see it as an opportunity to walk the bodhisattva path. Parents shouldn''t put pressure on their children by imposing their own expectations on them.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('KS5SSb_BO4w', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Birth (Part II: child-rearing)(GDD-28, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Children should be allowed to develop naturally and their education must be directed at their own characters and personal interests. Parental care and love should not be compromised by material compensation.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Gzg6EATBTFU', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Aging (Part I)(GDD-29, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Aging is not a problem as long as the elderly know how to take care of themselves, keep going with their willpower and aspirations, and continue to be of use by contributing their experience and wisdom while learning to let go.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('m96xSdw80e0', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Aging (Part II)(GDD-30, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Genuine youth is in the heart, not in the skin. Focus on the present and keep looking forward, and do away with the problem of being old by awakening the aspiration for enlightenment, dedicating oneself to sentient beings, and learning the bodhisattva spirit.\n.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('0t8cQH1EWas', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Illness(GDD-31, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Illness is normal and will help us develop a greater understanding of the process of life. We should view illness with detached observation and equanimity, as an experience to pay off our karmic debt.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('QI02ySfITDc', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Death (Part I)(GDD-32, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Death is a natural part of life and people have to be mentally prepared for it. Instead of feeling sorry we should recite Amitabha Buddha''s name for the dead. Letting go helps us overcome our fear for death and maintain our mental health.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('LSh_eid4G7I', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Death (Part I)(GDD-33, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Death is a natural part of life and people have to be mentally prepared for it. Instead of feeling sorry we should recite Amitabha Buddha''s name for the dead. Letting go helps us overcome our fear for death and maintain our mental health.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('f8XAk5bbsyA', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Death (Part III - Bardo: intermediate life entity)(GDD-34, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The best way to deliver the departed soul is to chant the Buddha''s name or recite Buddhist sutras, enabling their minds to become opened and free of attachments, and hopefully sending them to the Western Pure Land.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('ZuHxa00e-60', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Consulting the dead & delivering the deceased from suffering(GDD-35, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Prayer services and transfer of merit through providing charity and doing good deeds can benefit our departed loved ones. Buddhism advocates cremation, for it is the cleanest method and keeps the dead from clinging to their own bodies.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('FrHKGympm1U', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Greed(GDD-36, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Greed is when we want something we don''t need; it is the root of all our mental afflictions. Apply wisdom to distinguish between need and want. Seeking well-being for society and for all sentient beings is not greed.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('yInarZcqb0I', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Fame and fortune(GDD-37, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Ordinary people pursue fame and fortune out of greed. Buddhism tells us that these things are all empty. Success does not come from outside but lies within; it depends on whether you have a giving heart or are acting to serve society.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('0YXbwjOe_Gw', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Anger(GDD-38, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Anger comes when our greed cannot be satisfied or when things don''t go according to our wishes. It cannot resolve a problem and can lead to mental instability and physical illness. Instead, handle the problem with compassion and wisdom.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('p4e4npemmRI', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'How to eliminate ignorance and enhance wisdom(GDD-39, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Ignorance means our mental affliction and a lack of understanding of cause and effect, as well as causes and conditions; it means our inverted views. Ignorance is false and transitory; all living beings have transcendental wisdom, which is always there and has never changed.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('9cnCUddCvEU', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Arrogance and doubt(GDD-40, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Arrogance can happen when we think we are superior, or inferior, to others. To eliminate our arrogance we should not compare with anybody but should instead walk our own path and make our own efforts.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('6g6ws45yXxc', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Emotions(GDD-41, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Feelings often develop into emotions, which are irrational and can compromise our physical and mental health. We should dissolve our emotions by using reason, adjusting our concepts, or reciting the Buddha or bodhisattva''s name.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('ef9wkLpcO8o', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'The right ways of looking at love(GDD-42 Master Sheng Yen)', 'True love means giving, mutual support, mutual understanding, and mutual respect. A marital union is a two-way situation and requires the right causes and conditions.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('-8-_iHF521g', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Emotional adaptations during adolescence(GDD-43 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Young people in adolescence undergo huge physical and emotional changes. They need more understanding from their parents and teachers. By being friends with them, we can help them through sharing their feelings, and thus providing them with comfort and support.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('3TSLhPQuhl0', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Idol worship during adolescence(GDD-44 Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Idol worship during adolescence is normal, but the adult world has to change its business perspective in creating unorthodox people as role models and instead provide guidance to allow teenagers to admire great people and those who contribute to society.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('L6oIgwsEaqc', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Buddhism''s view on money (false speech) (GDD-45 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Greed and earning money are two separate things. Greed is selfish, while making money for the collective group, the family, society, and all the sentient beings, is not. Businessmen should make reasonable profit while paying back society.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Q6V9521C0cY', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Buddhism''s view on money (making charitable donations) (GDD-46 Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Giving benefits both others and oneself; it creates karmic merit, which becomes a blessing for oneself. Giving is not limited to money; one can also give of their knowledge, time, or physical strength to help others.\n \"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('-sULY8kX6Z8', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Buddhism and environmental protection(GDD-47 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Environmental protection reflects the Buddhist idea of purity, which encourages us to live a clean and simple way of life, as well as respect natural ecology and relish the blessings of Earth.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('RsYtcwUw9Fo', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Protecting the spiritual environment (GDD-48 Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Environmentalism is more than a concern of the physical environment and our living environment, it should also include our spiritual, psychological, and conceptual level. Protecting the spiritual environment lies in getting rid of selfishness.\n  \"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('ilZkSvBzBdc', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'Protecting the social environment(GDD-49 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Interpersonal relationships in life must start with etiquette and manners, which make human dignity and civilization possible. Respect and frugality are essential in practicing social environmentalism.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('7z4CuhWIDYU', 'PL9FA09E8B0E9F2E05', 'What''s the ultimate goal of Buddhism?(GDD-50 Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism helps people eliminate their suffering and live a happier life. Buddhist teachings are to be practiced in life. Chanting sutras and reciting the Buddha''s name can train the mind, develop faith and concentration.');
INSERT INTO playlist(pid, cid, title, description) VALUES('PL2EC967A506B50468','UCBIGwiecylJsQrhTPBKI4Qw', 'GDD(0001-0025)', 'GDD(0001-0025)');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('1O7ER7-C5-I', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'Buddhadharma in the Modern Era (GDD-1, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Ch''an practice lies in our daily life. Spiritual practice is to constantly pay attention to our action, speech, and thought, and correct ourselves, and therefore attain spiritual liberation and freedom of mind.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('c2OKNdAC7oI', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'The Functions of Meditation  (GDD-2, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Ch''an is not in sitting; it is about wisdom and letting go. But sitting meditation can help us keep a serene, stable body and mind, which in turn facilitates our Ch''an practice.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('k0bGu_hTEpQ', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'Chan Practice in Daily Life (Benefits of Chan Meditation) (GDD-3, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Meditation helps improve our work efficiency and emotions. Meditation requires relaxation in the body and mind, and guidance from an experienced teacher. One mustn''t expect instant results in practicing meditation.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('FO18Ac1sKt0', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'How to cope with and alleviate stress(GDD-4, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Stress is self imposed, and often results from not letting go. We will feel less stress by turning it into a self-expectation or aspiration, concentrating on the task at hand without being worried, and thinking of work as interesting life.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('DEgqrCfoByg', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'Must disputes and confrontations be settled through violence?(GDD-5, Master Sheng Yen)', 'In face of disputes and confrontations, instead of acting on our emotions and resorting to violence, we should use reason, patience, and compassion to dissolve the conflict and get along peacefully with others.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('seg7XM5Hzik', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'Diversity and karma(GDD-6, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Diversity reflects the working of causes and conditions, and natural principles, which are harmony and coordination. Diversity is normal, so we are required to consider and respect others by dissolving our ego.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('KKqmPSToWUU', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'Supernatural power and its impact on society(GDD-7, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Psychic ability and supernatural power do exist, which can be generated through spiritual practice. However, they cannot help one escape the law of cause and effect.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('kOrIWq0YgNw', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'How does Buddhism view the practice of fortune telling?(GDD-8, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Fortune telling and fengshui may have their validity and usefulness, but people can actually change their fate through psychological transformation and good deeds. What matters is the mind.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('VHxqyqmfVJ0', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'Reincarnation(GDD-9, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism believes in the concept of reincarnation, in which people are compelled, and must take responsibility for their own actions, whether of the body or of the mind.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('OFnPKIHx_4I', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'Karma—the notion of cause and effect(GDD-10, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Karma of the three periods of time refers to the causes and effects involved in the past, present, and future. In applying this concept in our daily life, we should always be aware of the consequences of our actions.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('nsuk8PU5fl4', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'Buddhism and family life(GDD-11, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Family problems come from a lack of sympathy and respect, and a lack of understanding of each other''s strengths and shortcomings. In engaging in spiritual practice at home, lay practitioners are required to first meet their responsibilities as a human being.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('4O-sUGS1pW4', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'How do householders practice spiritually? (GDD-12, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Householders can practice in daily life by cultivating discipline, concentration, and wisdom, that is, by following the five disciplines, maintaining a tranquil mind, and not clinging to the ego, which will help eliminate their vexations.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('PkYSwjz-d6Y', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'Effective communication between married couples (GDD-13, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Good family communication requires the couple to use the attitude of appreciation to listen to what each other wants to express, say more good words, more words of comfort and consolation, and say fewer words of complaint.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('nh_A2zKjvQc', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'How should married couples manage their money? (GDD-14, Master Sheng Yen)', 'In dealing with family financial matters, the husband and wife should consider whether the use of money is proper and whether the family income and expenditures should be balanced, and create a harmonious household by maintaining the family together.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('dA_npzsDf90', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'Responsibility of household chores (GDD-15, Master Sheng Yen)', 'In family life men and women are equal, in the sense that the husband and wife should share household work and cooperate, fulfilling their role as mother and father, taking up family responsibilities together.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Fi5wsS34rvo', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'Extramarital affair (GDD-16, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Extra-marital affairs bring psychological harm, a sense of insecurity, and fear, affecting one''s health and causing suffering. In facing the situation, no couple should take divorce lightly. The situation should be dealt with rationally.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('kAezCNutJLM', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'Marital violence (GDD-17, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Marital violence is related to the Buddhist concept of anger and hatred. Domestic violence can be avoided through introspection and self-examination, the attitudes of respect and caring, and  rational consideration and forgiveness.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('XRuIG34VMrc', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'Relationship with the in-laws (GDD-18, Master Sheng Yen)', 'In-law problems are also a generation gap, which often result in family discord. The fundamental solution is to respect others by surrendering one''s own ego and seeing another person from their position.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('0mzZ6xAtarU', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'The meaning of eating a vegetarian diet (Part I) (GDD-19, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism encourages people to eat a vegetarian diet not only for health and hygiene reasons, but mainly out of compassion and the belief that all sentient beings are equal.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Rsyj7m-11HI', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'The meaning of eating a vegetarian diet (Part II) (GDD-20, Master Sheng Yen)', '\"Meat imitation products are to tempt meat-eaters to try vegetarian food. Dairy products and unfertilized eggs are fine for vegetarians.\n\"');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('3wuiQHOeq1k', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'Taking of life of household insect pests(GDD-21, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Buddhism opposes killing in any form. In order to keep our surroundings clean, the best is a hygienic environment and using our intelligence to prevent pests, instead of killing living creatures afterwards.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('hCuNvwrfqUw', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'Abortion(GDD-22, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Human life actually begins from the moment of conception. A fetus has the right to life and is one''s own flesh and blood sharing a karmic connection or relation.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('HlXEROI0k1U', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'Euthanasia - an act of compassion or of cruelty?(GDD-23, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Aging, illness, and death are natural phenomena. It''s ideal that a person can just die naturally without human intervention. Religious faith can help one relax, and hence diminish one''s suffering, both physical and spiritual.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('Fs-LGVZEEKk', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'Setting animals free to save their lives(GDD-25, Master Sheng Yen)', 'Setting animals free is to reflect the Buddhist idea of compassion and respect for life. But it mustn''t end up encouraging hunters to go catch certain animals or disturbing the balance of natural ecology.');
INSERT INTO videos(vid, pid, title, description) VALUES('hcgMDa2LSWw', 'PL2EC967A506B50468', 'Suicide(GDD-24, Master Sheng Yen)', 'The human form is difficult to obtain and human life is precious. We obtain this body as a result of our karma and so should accept it and use it to repay our karmic debts or fulfill our vows as a duty.');
